.792B, a 11.12% increase year-over-year.\n\n**Earnings Performance:**\nNovo Nordisk reported its most recent earnings on Feb 4, 2026 for Q4 2025, posting earnings per share (EPS) of $1, which exceeded analysts' expectations of $0.89 by 12.36%.\n\n**Key Business Highlights:**\nNovo Nordisk reported 15% sales growth and 10% operating profit growth for the first 9 months of 2025. However, the company narrowed full-year guidance to sales growth of 8%–11% and operating profit growth of 4%–7% (constant exchange rates), citing lower-than-expected growth for GLP-1 treatments in diabetes and obesity and restructuring/transaction costs.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"56cadf2b-a7e5-4fc7-9037-6b601a7b78dc","uuid":"827ea1d0-7d47-4132-ad4e-dfa8d668e6fa","timestamp":"2026-04-28T16:54:06.152Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk NVO financial results FY2025 annual revenue earnings 2025","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01JWvNPkyezdvGvK3uo9HBox","content":[{"title":"Financial results and events overview - Novo Nordisk","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/investors/financial-results.html"},{"title":"Financial performance - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025","url":"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/strategic-aspirations/financial-performance.html"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/investors/annual-report.html"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Revenue 2012-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends","url":"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/revenue"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025 (PDF)","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/irmaterial/annual_report/2026/novo-nordisk-annual-report-2025.pdf"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S Common Stock (NVO) Earnings Report Dates & Earnings Forecasts | Nasdaq","url":"https://www.nasdaq.com/market-activity/stocks/nvo/earnings"},{"title":"Nov