{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01WmZtPt88j2ViWbuhERkpkX","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk Ozempic Wegovy revenue segment breakdown 2025\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Financial performance - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/strategic-aspirations/financial-performance.html\"},{\"title\":\"Slowing Ozempic, Wegovy sales lead to cut in top end of ...\",\"url\":\"https://firstwordpharma.com/story/6516083\"},{\"title\":\"Wegovy, Ozempic maker Novo Nordisk Q3 earnings; shares fall\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2025/11/05/wegovy-ozempic-maker-novo-nordisk-q3-earnings.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk predicts milder growth in 2025 after obesity star Wegovy doubles sales in Q4 | Fierce Pharma\",\"url\":\"https://www.fiercepharma.com/pharma/novo-nordisk-predicts-milder-sales-growth-2025-after-obesity-star-wegovy-doubles-numbers-q4\"},{\"title\":\"Q3-investor-presentation-2025.pdf\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/pdfs/financial-results/2025/Q3-investor-presentation-2025.pdf\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Q3 Earnings & Revenues Miss, GLP-1 Drugs Face US Hurdles\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/novo-nordisk-q3-earnings-revenues-153000106.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Semaglutide Revenue: How Ozempic and Wegovy Are Driving Record Profits - Pharmacy Business Hub\",\"url\":\"https://pharmabusinesshub.com/novo-nordisk-semaglutide-revenue/\"},{\"title\":\"Financial report for the period 1 January 2025 to 30 September 2025\",\"url\":\"https://ml-eu.globenewswire.com/Resource/Download/ae93d17e-6c68-433e-ac46-9ea814575af0\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk cuts 2025 forecast amid slower GLP-1 sales\",\"url\":\"https://www.emarketer.com/content/slower-growing-glp-1-drug-sales-force-novo-nordisk-cut-forecast-again\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk: Wegovy sales by quarter 2025\",\"url\":\"https://www.statista.com/statistics/1416998/sales-wegovy-novo-nordisk-by-quarter/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's information about Novo Nordisk's Ozempic and Wegovy revenue in 2025:\n\n## 2025 Revenue Performance\n\n**Ozempic (Diabetes):**\nOzempic sales increased by 6% measured in Danish kroner and by 10% at constant exchange rates (CER) to DKK 127,089 million for the full year 2025. For Q3 2025 alone, Ozempic recorded sales of DKK 30.74 billion, up 9%.\n\n**Wegovy (Obesity Care):**\nWegovy sales rose 18% year-on-year in Q3 2025 to hit 20.35 billion Danish kroner. Obesity Care (Saxenda and Wegovy) sales were up 18% to DKK 21.11 billion in Q3 2025.\n\n## Segment Breakdown\n\nFor the first nine months of 2025, sales grew by 12% measured in Danish kroner and by 15% at CER in the first nine months of 2025, driven by Obesity care sales growth of 41% (CER), driven by Wegovy and Diabetes care sales growth of 8% (CER), driven by Ozempic.\n\n## Growth Challenges\n\nDespite strong sales volumes, Diabetes and obesity care were a key growth driver following the uptake of Wegovy and Ozempic, however the company lowered its expectations for growth, citing prescription trends, competition and pricing pressure. Wegovy's sales growth rate continues to slow, with third-quarter sales reaching DKK 20.35 billion, up 23%, as growth was impacted by the availability of illegal compounded versions in Novo Nordisk's largest obesity market, the United States, as well as increased competition from Eli Lilly.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"56cadf2b-a7e5-4fc7-9037-6b601a7b78dc","uuid":"3c52f7d8-10a0-4dae-8424-654522e4a9ff","timestamp":"2026-04-28T16:54:10.313Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk Ozempic Wegovy revenue segment breakdown 2025","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01Ptok52FBQnns3XdAmtNrR9","content":[{"title":"Financial performance - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025","url":"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/strategic-aspirations/financial-performance.html"},{"title":"Slowing Ozempic, Wegovy sales lead to cut in top end of ...","url":"https://firstwordpharma.com/story/6516083"},{"title":"Wegovy, Ozempic maker Novo Nordisk Q3 earnings; shares fall","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2025/11/05/wegovy-ozempic-maker-novo-nordisk-q3-earnings.html"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk predicts milder growth in 2025 after obesity star Wegovy doubles sales in Q4 | Fierce Pharma","url":"https://www.fiercepharma.com/pharma/novo-nordisk-predicts-milder-sales-growth-2025-after-obesity-star-wegovy-doubles-numbers-q4"},{"title":"Q3-investor-presentation-2025.pdf","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/pdfs/financial-results/2025/Q3-investor-presentation-2025.pdf"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Q3 Earnings & Revenues Miss, GLP-1 Drugs Face US Hurdles","url":"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/novo-nordisk-q3-earnings-revenues-153000106.html"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Semaglutide Revenue: How Ozempic and Wegovy Are Driving Record Profits - Pharmacy Business Hub","url":"https://pharmabusinesshub.com/novo-nordisk-semaglutide-revenue/"},{"title":"Financial report for the period 1 January 2025 to 30 September 2025","url":"https://ml-eu.globenewswire.com/Resource/Download/ae93d17e-6c68-433e-ac46-9ea814575af0"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk cuts 2025 forecast amid slower GLP-1 sales","url":"https://www.emarketer.com/content/slower-growing-glp-1-drug-sales-force-novo-nordisk-cut-forecast-again"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk: Wegovy sales by quarter 2025","url":"https://www.statista.com/statistics/1416998/sales-wegovy-novo-nordisk-by-quarter/"}]},"Based on the search results, here's information about Novo Nordisk's Ozempic and Wegovy revenue in 2025:\n\n## 2025 Revenue Performance\n\n**Ozempic (Diabetes):**\nOzempic sales increased by 6% measured in Danish kroner and by 10% at constant exchange rates (CER) to DKK 127,089 million for the full year 2025. For Q3 2025 alone, Ozempic recorded sales of DKK 30.74 billion, up 9%.\n\n**Wegovy (Obesity Care):**\nWegovy sales rose 18% year-on-year in Q3 2025 to hit 20.35 billion Danish kroner. Obesity Care (Saxenda and Wegovy) sales were up 18% to DKK 21.11 billion in Q3 2025.\n\n## Segment Breakdown\n\nFor the first nine months of 2025, sales grew by 12% measured in Danish kroner and by 15% at CER in the first nine months of 2025, driven by Obesity care sales growth of 41% (CER), driven by Wegovy and Diabetes care sales growth of 8% (CER), driven by Ozempic.\n\n## Growth Challenges\n\nDespite strong sales volumes, Diabetes and obesity care were a key growth driver following the uptake of Wegovy and Ozempic, however the company lowered its expectations for growth, citing prescription trends, competition and pricing pressure. Wegovy's sales growth rate continues to slow, with third-quarter sales reaching DKK 20.35 billion, up 23%, as growth was impacted by the availability of illegal compounded versions in Novo Nordisk's largest obesity market, the United States, as well as increased competition from Eli Lilly."],"durationSeconds":7.964376666}}
