{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_011Q1RjE232i6gWQSbmaRGCP","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk NVO balance sheet total assets debt equity 2024 2025\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Balance Sheet & Financial Health Metrics - Simply Wall St\",\"url\":\"https://simplywall.st/stocks/us/pharmaceuticals-biotech/nyse-nvo/novo-nordisk/health\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Balance Sheet - Yahoo Finance\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NVO/balance-sheet/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Total Assets 2012-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends\",\"url\":\"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/total-assets\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Balance Sheet\",\"url\":\"https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/nvo/financials/balance-sheet/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk ADR (NVO) Balance Sheet - Investing.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.investing.com/equities/novo-nordis-balance-sheet\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/investors/annual-report.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Balance Sheet 2011-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends\",\"url\":\"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/balance-sheet\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Stock Financials: Balance Sheet | Seeking Alpha\",\"url\":\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVO/balance-sheet\"},{\"title\":\"NYSE:NVO Financials | Novo Nordisk - Investing.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.investing.com/equities/novo-nordis-financial-summary\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Financials 2026 - Income Statement and Balance Sheet $NVO\",\"url\":\"https://www.marketbeat.com/stocks/NYSE/NVO/financials/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's the balance sheet information for Novo Nordisk (NVO):\n\n## Total Assets\nNovo Nordisk total assets for 2024 were $67.54B, a 47.91% increase from 2023. More recently, total assets for the quarter ending September 30, 2025 were $80.224B, a 36.94% increase year-over-year.\n\n## Debt and Equity\nNovo Nordisk has a total shareholder equity of DKK194.0B and total debt of DKK122.4B, which brings its debt-to-equity ratio to 63.1%. Additionally, its total assets and total liabilities are DKK542.9B and DKK348.9B respectively.\n\n## Latest Quarterly Data (Q1 2025)\nNovo Nordisk total assets for Q1 2025 were $85.42B, a increase of 6.02% from the previous quarter.\n\nThese figures show significant growth in Novo Nordisk's total assets year-over-year, with a strong balance sheet characterized by a moderate debt-to-equity ratio.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"56cadf2b-a7e5-4fc7-9037-6b601a7b78dc","uuid":"6f3446c0-9f66-4af9-84ee-304625675b05","timestamp":"2026-04-28T16:54:19.684Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk NVO balance sheet total assets debt equity 2024 2025","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01VCkTDqH9Z3Wtuv8XjPuftq","content":[{"title":"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Balance Sheet & Financial Health Metrics - Simply Wall St","url":"https://simplywall.st/stocks/us/pharmaceuticals-biotech/nyse-nvo/novo-nordisk/health"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Balance Sheet - Yahoo Finance","url":"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NVO/balance-sheet/"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Total Assets 2012-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends","url":"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/total-assets"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Balance Sheet","url":"https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/nvo/financials/balance-sheet/"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk ADR (NVO) Balance Sheet - Investing.com","url":"https://www.investing.com/equities/novo-nordis-balance-sheet"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/investors/annual-report.html"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Balance Sheet 2011-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends","url":"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/balance-sheet"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Stock Financials: Balance Sheet | Seeking Alpha","url":"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVO/balance-sheet"},{"title":"NYSE:NVO Financials | Novo Nordisk - Investing.com","url":"https://www.investing.com/equities/novo-nordis-financial-summary"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Financials 2026 - Income Statement and Balance Sheet $NVO","url":"https://www.marketbeat.com/stocks/NYSE/NVO/financials/"}]},"Based on the search results, here's the balance sheet information for Novo Nordisk (NVO):\n\n## Total Assets\nNovo Nordisk total assets for 2024 were $67.54B, a 47.91% increase from 2023. More recently, total assets for the quarter ending September 30, 2025 were $80.224B, a 36.94% increase year-over-year.\n\n## Debt and Equity\nNovo Nordisk has a total shareholder equity of DKK194.0B and total debt of DKK122.4B, which brings its debt-to-equity ratio to 63.1%. Additionally, its total assets and total liabilities are DKK542.9B and DKK348.9B respectively.\n\n## Latest Quarterly Data (Q1 2025)\nNovo Nordisk total assets for Q1 2025 were $85.42B, a increase of 6.02% from the previous quarter.\n\nThese figures show significant growth in Novo Nordisk's total assets year-over-year, with a strong balance sheet characterized by a moderate debt-to-equity ratio."],"durationSeconds":4.701035041000003}}
