cial performance - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/strategic-aspirations/financial-performance.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Revenue 2012-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends\",\"url\":\"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/revenue\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/investors/annual-report.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk EPS - Earnings per Share 2012-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends\",\"url\":\"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/eps-earnings-per-share-diluted\"},{\"title\":\"Financial results and events overview - Novo Nordisk\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/investors/financial-results.html\"},{\"title\":\"Financials - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2024\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2024/strategic-aspirations/financials.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025 (PDF)\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/irmaterial/annual_report/2026/novo-nordisk-annual-report-2025.pdf\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Net Income 2012-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends\",\"url\":\"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/net-income\"},{\"title\":\"NVO 2026 Earnings & EPS History - Quarterly & Annual Growth Reports\",\"url\":\"https://fullratio.com/stocks/nyse-nvo/earnings\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) - Revenue\",\"url\":\"https://companiesmarketcap.com/novo-nordisk/revenue/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results from Novo Nordisk's FY2025 Annual Report, here are the key income statement figures:\n\n## FY2025 Income Statement Summary\n\n**Sales/Revenue:**\n- Sales increased by 6% measured in Danish kroner and by 10% at CER to DKK 309,064 million in 2025\n- Revenue for the twelve months ending December 31, 2025 was $46.792B, a 11.12% increase year-over-year\n\n**Operating Profit:**\n- Operating profit decreased by 1% measured in Danish kroner and increased by 6% at CER to DKK 127,658 million\n- This was mainly impacted by one-off restructuring costs related to the company-wide transformation during the third quarter of around DKK 8 billion\n\n**Net Income:**\n- Net profit increased by 1% to DKK 102,434 million\n- Net income for the twelve months ending December 31, 2025 was $15.509B, a 5.91% increase year-over-year\n\n**Earnings Per Share (EPS):**\n- Diluted earnings per share increased by 2% to DKK 23.03\n- EPS for the twelve months ending December 31, 2025 was $3.49, a 6.28% increase year-over-year\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"56cadf2b-a7e5-4fc7-9037-6b601a7b78dc","uuid":"4688641c-f56f-4701-90ca-ca771cc1eb05","timestamp":"2026-04-28T16:54:21.943Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk FY2025 annual report income statement operating profit net income EPS DKK USD 2025","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01VFdkti5o6BZoTEiXeM4W5i","content":[{"title":"Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/investors/annual-report.html"},{"title":"Financial results and events overview - Novo Nordisk","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/investors/financial-results.html"},{"title":"Financial performance - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025","url":"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/strategic-aspirations/financial-performance.html"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Revenue 2012-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends","url":"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/revenue"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025 (PDF)","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/irmaterial/annual_report/2026/novo-nordisk-annual-report-2025.pdf"},{"title":"Financials - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2024","url":"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2024/strategic-aspirations/financials.html"},{"title":"securities and exchange commission","url":"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/353278/00