{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01EZaq3jNDRYy2d36kjRS8LB","type":"tool_result","content":"# Novo Nordisk Financial Metrics - FY2025 vs FY2024\n\n## Revenue by Segment (FY2025)\n\n**Obesity Care:** DKK 82.3 billion (↑26% DKK / ↑31% CER)\n- \"Sales of Obesity care products increased by 26% measured in Danish kroner\"\n\n**Diabetes Care:** DKK 207.1 billion (flat DKK / ↑4% CER)\n- \"Sales in Diabetes care remained unchanged in Danish kroner and increased by 4% at CER\"\n\n**Rare Disease:** DKK 19.6 billion (↑5% DKK / ↑9% CER)\n\n**Total Sales:** DKK 309.1 billion (↑6% DKK / ↑10% CER)\n\n## Profitability Metrics\n\n| Metric | FY2025 | FY2024 | Change |\n|--------|--------|--------|--------|\n| Operating Profit | DKK 127.7 billion | DKK 128.7 billion | -1% DKK / +6% CER |\n| Net Profit | DKK 102.4 billion | DKK 101.4 billion | +1% |\n| Gross Margin | 81.0% | 84.7% | -370 bps |\n| Diluted EPS | DKK 23.03 | DKK 22.58 | +2% |\n\n## Key Expense Areas (FY2025)\n\n- **Cost of Goods Sold:** DKK 58.8 billion (↑32%)\n- **R&D Expenses:** DKK 52.0 billion (↑8% / ↑10% CER) at 16.8% of sales\n- **Sales & Distribution:** DKK 64.3 billion (↑4%) at 20.8% of sales\n\n## Cash Flow\n\n**Free Cash Flow:** DKK 28.3 billion (2025) vs DKK -14.7 billion (2024)\n- \"Capital expenditure for property, plant and equipment was DKK 60.1 billion\""}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"56cadf2b-a7e5-4fc7-9037-6b601a7b78dc","uuid":"643c6bea-0019-469e-a4a5-1c82051ca2f1","timestamp":"2026-04-28T16:54:32.434Z","tool_use_result":{"bytes":386579,"code":200,"codeText":"OK","result":"# Novo Nordisk Financial Metrics - FY2025 vs FY2024\n\n## Revenue by Segment (FY2025)\n\n**Obesity Care:** DKK 82.3 billion (↑26% DKK / ↑31% CER)\n- \"Sales of Obesity care products increased by 26% measured in Danish kroner\"\n\n**Diabetes Care:** DKK 207.1 billion (flat DKK / ↑4% CER)\n- \"Sales in Diabetes care remained unchanged in Danish kroner and increased by 4% at CER\"\n\n**Rare Disease:** DKK 19.6 billion (↑5% DKK / ↑9% CER)\n\n**Total Sales:** DKK 309.1 billion (↑6% DKK / ↑10% CER)\n\n## Profitability Metrics\n\n| Metric | FY2025 | FY2024 | Change |\n|--------|--------|--------|--------|\n| Operating Profit | DKK 127.7 billion | DKK 128.7 billion | -1% DKK / +6% CER |\n| Net Profit | DKK 102.4 billion | DKK 101.4 billion | +1% |\n| Gross Margin | 81.0% | 84.7% | -370 bps |\n| Diluted EPS | DKK 23.03 | DKK 22.58 | +2% |\n\n## Key Expense Areas (FY2025)\n\n- **Cost of Goods Sold:** DKK 58.8 billion (↑32%)\n- **R&D Expenses:** DKK 52.0 billion (↑8% / ↑10% CER) at 16.8% of sales\n- **Sales & Distribution:** DKK 64.3 billion (↑4%) at 20.8% of sales\n\n## Cash Flow\n\n**Free Cash Flow:** DKK 28.3 billion (2025) vs DKK -14.7 billion (2024)\n- \"Capital expenditure for property, plant and equipment was DKK 60.1 billion\"","durationMs":6650,"url":"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/strategic-aspirations/financial-performance.html"}}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01BqXmP3RyW6GU4SEJeLCubH","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk competitive moat GLP-1 pipeline competitors Eli Lilly Rybelsus semaglutide CagriSema 2025 2026\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"What is Competitive Landscape of Novo Nordisk Company? – PortersFiveForce.com\",\"url\":\"https://portersfiveforce.com/blogs/competitors/novonordisk\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk vs Eli Lilly: Who’s Winning the Obesity Drug Race?\",\"url\":\"https://www.delveinsight.com/blog/novo-vs-eli-lilly-in-anti-obesity-drug-market\"},{\"title\":\"Eli Lilly's GLP-1 growth is only getting started as Novo Nordisk braces for a decline in 2026\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/02/04/eli-lilly-novo-nordisk-earnings-glp1-market.html\"},{\"title\":\"Eli Lilly vs. Novo Nordisk: The Obesity Drug Race Has a New Leader - 24/7 Wall St.\",\"url\":\"https://247wallst.com/investing/2026/04/10/eli-lilly-vs-novo-nordisk-the-obesity-drug-race-has-a-new-leader/\"},{\"title\":\"The leading GLP-1 contenders in pharma’s race for an obesity pill | PharmaVoice\",\"url\":\"https://www.pharmavoice.com/news/glp-1-pharma-obesity-pill-drug-novo-viking-structure-lilly/808195/\"},{\"title\":\"Eli Lilly vs Novo Nordisk: Which Obesity Drug Stock Is the Better Buy? | The Motley Fool\",\"url\":\"https://www.fool.com/investing/2026/03/27/eli-lilly-vs-novo-nordisk-which-obesity-drug-stock/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo beats Lilly to first FDA-approved GLP-1RA pill for obesity - Pharmaceutical Technology\",\"url\":\"https://www.pharmaceutical-technology.com/news/novo-beats-lilly-to-first-fda-approved-glp-1ra-pill-for-obesity/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk: Engineering a Comeback for a Strong 2026 Trajectory\",\"url\":\"https://biotechinvestor25.substack.com/p/novo-nordisk-engineering-a-comeback\"},{\"title\":\"Novo regained weight loss footing in the pill arena — but Lilly is coming | PharmaVoice\",\"url\":\"https://www.pharmavoice.com/news/novo-lilly-weight-loss-glp-1-pill/814604/\"},{\"title\":\"Lilly vs. Novo Nordisk: Obesity Drug Giants' Face-Off in 2026 — TradingView News\",\"url\":\"https://www.tradingview.com/news/zacks:879758555094b:0-lilly-vs-novo-nordisk-obesity-drug-giants-face-off-in-2026/\"}]\n\nI've completed the web search on Novo Nordisk's competitive position in the GLP-1 market. Here's a summary of the key findings:\n\n## Novo Nordisk's Competitive Moat\n\nNovo's competitive moat is built on strategic moves that pair clinical leadership in GLP-1 outcomes with deep payer relationships, creating durable commercial advantage in obesity and diabetes. The company's competitive edge rests on scale in peptide manufacturing, a differentiated outcomes profile for semaglutide brands, and a rich next-wave incretin pipeline (CagriSema, amycretin, oral incretins) that targets incremental efficacy and patient segments.\n\n## Current Pipeline and Products\n\n**Semaglutide Products:** Semaglutide programs (Ozempic/Wegovy/Rybelsus) benefit from extensive outcomes data and a 2024 US Wegovy label update for cardiovascular risk reduction in adults with obesity and CVD, strengthening payer coverage and prescribing preference.\n\n**CagriSema:** CagriSema, a powerful combination of semaglutide and cagrilintide, is designed to enhance appetite suppression and improve metabolic control. However, early weight loss trial results suggest CagriSema performs better than Wegovy alone, but it has fallen short of investor and executive expectations, with Novo missing its 25% weight loss target in December.\n\n**Oral Wegovy:** The Wegovy pill launched in January 2026 across 70,000-plus pharmacies and is generating roughly 50,000 weekly prescriptions.\n\n## Competitive Threats from Eli Lilly\n\nTirzepatide (in Zepbound and Mounjaro) is \"superior\" in its effectiveness and tolerability compared to semaglutide, a claim proven in a head-to-head clinical trial conducted by Lilly in 2024. If Lilly receives orforglipron approval in the U.S. by mid-2026, it enters the oral market with a product that has already beaten oral semaglutide in a head-to-head trial.\n\nWhile Novo said expiring patents in some international markets pose a challenge, Lilly's tirzepatide should be protected into \"the back half of the 2030s\" in major markets.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"56cadf2b-a7e5-4fc7-9037-6b601a7b78dc","uuid":"e2231281-accc-4a2e-812a-2d67e7824bf8","timestamp":"2026-04-28T16:54:36.655Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk competitive moat GLP-1 pipeline competitors Eli Lilly Rybelsus semaglutide CagriSema 2025 2026","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01PCeuaLRDGw4mbEt4tAbgFA","content":[{"title":"What is Competitive Landscape of Novo Nordisk Company? – PortersFiveForce.com","url":"https://portersfiveforce.com/blogs/competitors/novonordisk"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk vs Eli Lilly: Who’s Winning the Obesity Drug Race?","url":"https://www.delveinsight.com/blog/novo-vs-eli-lilly-in-anti-obesity-drug-market"},{"title":"Eli Lilly's GLP-1 growth is only getting started as Novo Nordisk braces for a decline in 2026","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/02/04/eli-lilly-novo-nordisk-earnings-glp1-market.html"},{"title":"Eli Lilly vs. Novo Nordisk: The Obesity Drug Race Has a New Leader - 24/7 Wall St.","url":"https://247wallst.com/investing/2026/04/10/eli-lilly-vs-novo-nordisk-the-obesity-drug-race-has-a-new-leader/"},{"title":"The leading GLP-1 contenders in pharma’s race for an obesity pill | PharmaVoice","url":"https://www.pharmavoice.com/news/glp-1-pharma-obesity-pill-drug-novo-viking-structure-lilly/808195/"},{"title":"Eli Lilly vs Novo Nordisk: Which Obesity Drug Stock Is the Better Buy? | The Motley Fool","url":"https://www.fool.com/investing/2026/03/27/eli-lilly-vs-novo-nordisk-which-obesity-drug-stock/"},{"title":"Novo beats Lilly to first FDA-approved GLP-1RA p