its 25% weight loss target in December.\n\n**Oral Wegovy:** The Wegovy pill launched in January 2026 across 70,000-plus pharmacies and is generating roughly 50,000 weekly prescriptions.\n\n## Competitive Threats from Eli Lilly\n\nTirzepatide (in Zepbound and Mounjaro) is \"superior\" in its effectiveness and tolerability compared to semaglutide, a claim proven in a head-to-head clinical trial conducted by Lilly in 2024. If Lilly receives orforglipron approval in the U.S. by mid-2026, it enters the oral market with a product that has already beaten oral semaglutide in a head-to-head trial.\n\nWhile Novo said expiring patents in some international markets pose a challenge, Lilly's tirzepatide should be protected into \"the back half of the 2030s\" in major markets."],"durationSeconds":9.371912624999997}}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_019PiPVJX4Q5gSnmM3N9zhe3","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk CEO Lars Fruergaard Jorgensen management team compensation ownership 2025 proxy\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Company announcement\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/nncorp/global/en/news-and-media/news-and-ir-materials/news-details.html?id=916408\"},{\"title\":\"Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen - Wikipedia\",\"url\":\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lars_Fruergaard_J%C3%B8rgensen\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Names New CEO; Makes Other Leadership Changes - DCAT Value Chain Insights\",\"url\":\"https://www.dcatvci.org/top-industry-news/novo-nordisk-names-new-ceo-makes-other-leadership-changes/\"},{\"title\":\"Will New CEO's Leadership Propel Novo Nordisk's Next Growth Wave?\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/ceos-leadership-propel-novo-nordisks-130600201.html\"},{\"title\":\"Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/about/executive-management/lars-fruergaard-jorgensen.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NOVO B) Leadership & Management Team Analysis - Simply Wall St\",\"url\":\"https://simplywall.st/stocks/dk/pharmaceuticals-biotech/cph-novo-b/novo-nordisk-shares/management\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk CEO Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen to Step Down Amid Strategic Leadership Transition | PharmExec\",\"url\":\"https://www.pharmexec.com/view/novo-nordisk-ceo-lars-fruergaard-jorgensen-step-down-strategic-leadership-transition\"},{\"title\":\"Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen | ISPE | International Society for Pharmaceutical Engineering\",\"url\":\"https://ispe.org/people/lars-fruergaard-jorgensen\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Leadership & Management Team Analysis - Simply Wall St\",\"url\":\"https://simplywall.st/stocks/us/pharmaceuticals-biotech/nyse-nvo/novo-nordisk/management\"},{\"title\":\"Novo to part ways with longtime CEO Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen, citing weight of market pressures\",\"url\":\"https://www.fiercepharma.com/pharma/novo-part-ways-longtime-ceo-lars-fruergaard-jorgensen-citing-weight-market-pressures\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what I found regarding Novo Nordisk's leadership and related information:\n\n## CEO Transition\n\nMaziar Mike Doustdar was appointed as president and chief executive officer effective August 7, 2025, succeeding Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen, who stepped down on the same date. Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen was the chief executive of Novo Nordisk between January 2017 and August 2025.\n\n## New CEO Background\n\nMike Doustdar, currently Novo Nordisk's executive vice president of International Operations, has a strong track record of creating value and driving growth, with Novo Nordisk's International Operations more than doubling sales to approximately DKK 112 billion in 2024 under his leadership over the past decade.\n\n## Management Ownership\n\nNovo Nordisk's CEO Maziar Doustdar, appointed in August 2025, directly owns 0.002% of the company's shares, worth DKK20.10M.\n\n## Other Executive Changes\n\nEmil Kongshøj Larsen, currently senior vice president of the Europe and Canada region (EUCAN), will join Executive Management and succeed Mike Doustdar, assuming the responsibility of executive vice president, International Operations. Novo Nordisk decided to merge Research & Early Development with its Development area into a new, consolidated R&D unit under the leadership of Martin Holst Lange, who was appointed chief scientific officer effective August 7.\n\nThe search results do not contain specific information about compensation details or the 2025 proxy statement for the management team.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"56cadf2b-a7e5-4fc7-9037-6b601a7b78dc","uuid":"66968ace-c207-48c5-b582-e0326fd0fcca","timestamp":"2026-04-28T16:54:41.143Z","tool_use_result":{"que