{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01YD1gLvDgioQpf62EUUy1g4","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk NVO free cash flow capex 2022 2023 2024 2025 annual\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Free Cash Flow 2012-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends\",\"url\":\"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/free-cash-flow\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Free Cash Flow Per Share 2011-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends\",\"url\":\"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/free-cash-flow-per-share\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Cash Flow Statement\",\"url\":\"https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/nvo/financials/cash-flow-statement/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Free Cash Flow - Current & Historical Data (Dec 2025)\",\"url\":\"https://www.financecharts.com/stocks/NVO/growth/free-cash-flow\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Price to Free Cash Flow Ratio 2012-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends\",\"url\":\"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/price-fcf\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Cash Flow - Yahoo Finance - Yahoo Finance\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NVO/cash-flow/\"},{\"title\":\"NVO (Novo Nordisk AS) Free Cash Flow per Share\",\"url\":\"https://www.gurufocus.com/term/free-cash-flow-per-share/NVO\"},{\"title\":\"Financials - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2024\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2024/strategic-aspirations/financials.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Cash Flow from Operating Activities 2011-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends\",\"url\":\"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/cash-flow-from-operating-activities\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) - Free Cash Flow (Annual)\",\"url\":\"https://www.alphaquery.com/stock/NVO/fundamentals/annual/free-cash-flow\"}]\n\nBased on the web search results, here's the information on Novo Nordisk's free cash flow and capital expenditures:\n\n## Free Cash Flow (Annual)\n\n- Novo Nordisk annual free cash flow for 2024 was $10.702B, a 11.31% decline from 2023\n- Novo Nordisk annual free cash flow for 2023 was $12.066B, a 27.68% increase from 2022\n\nNote: There's a discrepancy in the 2024 figures depending on currency. Free cash flow in 2024 was realised at DKK -14.7 billion compared to DKK 68.3 billion in 2023. The lower free cash flow in 2024 is mainly impacted by the USD 11.7 billion acquisition price related to the three Catalent manufacturing sites.\n\n## Capital Expenditures\n\nFrom the Yahoo Finance data, capital expenditures were:\n- 2024: $90.113 billion\n- 2023: $51.309 billion\n- 2022: $38.896 billion\n\n## Operating Cash Flow\n\nFor context:\n- Novo Nordisk annual cash flow from operating activities for 2024 was $17.54B, a 10.92% increase from 2023\n- Novo Nordisk annual cash flow from operating activities for 2023 was $15.813B, a 41.57% increase from 2022\n\nNote: 2025 data appears to only be available as trailing twelve months or estimates at this time.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"56cadf2b-a7e5-4fc7-9037-6b601a7b78dc","uuid":"ae394c94-610d-4b4d-866c-489466242f97","timestamp":"2026-04-28T16:54:54.229Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk NVO free cash flow capex 2022 2023 2024 2025 annual","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_018AbYSkJAkNsM1bjpsbzw3j","content":[{"title":"Novo Nordisk Free Cash Flow 2012-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends","url":"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/free-cash-flow"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Free Cash Flow Per Share 2011-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends","url":"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/free-cash-flow-per-share"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Cash Flow Statement","url":"https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/nvo/financials/cash-flow-statement/"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Free Cash Flow - Current & Historical Data (Dec 2025)","url":"https://www.financecha