{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01NLwvmSHNf2oomDj1ZR16F8","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk NVO valuation P/E EV/EBITDA peer comparison Eli Lilly AstraZeneca 2026\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"NVO (Novo Nordisk A/S) vs LLY (Eli Lilly and Co) Comparison - Alpha Spread\",\"url\":\"https://www.alphaspread.com/comparison/nyse/nvo/vs/nyse/lly\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NYSE:NVO) Stock Valuation, Peer Comparison & Price Targets - Simply Wall St\",\"url\":\"https://simplywall.st/stocks/us/pharmaceuticals-biotech/nyse-nvo/novo-nordisk/valuation\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Stock Analysis & Key Metrics (2026)\",\"url\":\"https://koalagains.com/stocks/NYSE/NVO\"},{\"title\":\"I Expect Novo Nordisk To Outperform Eli Lilly In 2026: Here's Why | Seeking Alpha\",\"url\":\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4857159-i-expect-novo-nordisk-to-outperform-eli-lilly-in-2026-heres-why\"},{\"title\":\"Skip The Market Darling Eli Lilly; Buy The Underdog Novo Nordisk (NYSE:NVO) | Seeking Alpha\",\"url\":\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4852027-skip-the-market-darling-eli-lilly-buy-the-underdog-novo-nordisk\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Statistics & Valuation\",\"url\":\"https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/nvo/statistics/\"},{\"title\":\"Eli Lilly Vs. Novo Nordisk: The Valuation Gap Is Unreasonable (NYSE:NVO) | Seeking Alpha\",\"url\":\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4876511-eli-lilly-vs-novo-nordisk-the-valuation-gap-is-unreasonable\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Valuation Measures & Financial Statistics\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NVO/key-statistics/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Has Fallen 56% From Its High. Is NVO Finally Cheap Enough to Buy in 2026? | TIKR.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.tikr.com/blog/novo-nordisk-has-fallen-56-from-its-high-is-nvo-finally-cheap-enough-to-buy-in-2026\"},{\"title\":\"NVO 2026 Earnings & EPS History - Quarterly & Annual Growth Reports\",\"url\":\"https://fullratio.com/stocks/nyse-nvo/earnings\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's a comprehensive overview of Novo Nordisk's valuation metrics compared to peer companies:\n\n## P/E Ratio Comparison\n\nNVO is good value based on its Price-To-Earnings Ratio (11.4x) compared to the peer average (19.3x). More specifically, NVO's TTM P/E ratio is 12.4, which is considerably lower than the peer average for big pharma, which often ranges from 17x to 20x.\n\nIn peer comparisons, NVO's TTM EV/EBITDA multiple of 9.14 is modest compared to peers like Johnson & Johnson (15.1x) and Eli Lilly (33.3x). Meanwhile, Eli Lilly trades at an NTM EV/EBITDA of 20.72x and an NTM P/E of 26.13x.\n\n## EV/EBITDA Analysis\n\nThe most recent data shows the stock's EV/EBITDA ratio is 8.17, while other sources cite valuation ratios with an EV/EBITDA of 10.59x and P/E of 14.26x, suggesting the stock is attractively priced relative to its earnings and cash flows.\n\nFor additional context on peers: Roche trades at 10.81x NTM EV/EBITDA and Novartis sits at 13.29x.\n\n## Overall Valuation Assessment\n\nNVO stock trades at a multi-year low P/E, maintains high profitability, a strong balance sheet, and consistent EPS growth, making it a compelling 2026 recovery candidate.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"56cadf2b-a7e5-4fc7-9037-6b601a7b78dc","uuid":"dc46b4ed-0595-49b0-b3f3-5165631a6881","timestamp":"2026-04-28T16:54:54.902Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk NVO valuation P/E EV/EBITDA peer comparison Eli Lilly AstraZeneca 2026","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01P5DjpseATAX2pzW2QwiPoc","content":[{"title":"NVO (Novo Nordisk A/S) vs LLY (Eli Lilly and Co) Comparison - Alpha Spread","url":"https://www.alphaspread.com/comparison/nyse/nvo/vs/nyse/lly"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk (NYSE:NVO) Stock Valuation, Peer Comparison & Price Targets - Simply Wall St","url":"https://