nwhile, Eli Lilly trades at an NTM EV/EBITDA of 20.72x and an NTM P/E of 26.13x.\n\n## EV/EBITDA Analysis\n\nThe most recent data shows the stock's EV/EBITDA ratio is 8.17, while other sources cite valuation ratios with an EV/EBITDA of 10.59x and P/E of 14.26x, suggesting the stock is attractively priced relative to its earnings and cash flows.\n\nFor additional context on peers: Roche trades at 10.81x NTM EV/EBITDA and Novartis sits at 13.29x.\n\n## Overall Valuation Assessment\n\nNVO stock trades at a multi-year low P/E, maintains high profitability, a strong balance sheet, and consistent EPS growth, making it a compelling 2026 recovery candidate."],"durationSeconds":7.068943791999998}}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_012CyNkEzdmxHPMnRojkCb8Q","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk NVO risks 2025 2026 CagriSema failure tariffs Medicare drug pricing compounding GLP-1\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"The Valuation Reset: A Deep-Dive into Novo Nordisk (NVO) in 2026\",\"url\":\"https://markets.financialcontent.com/wral/article/finterra-2026-2-27-the-valuation-reset-a-deep-dive-into-novo-nordisk-nvo-in-2026\"},{\"title\":\"FinancialContent - The Valuation Reset: A Deep-Dive into Novo Nordisk (NVO) in 2026\",\"url\":\"https://markets.financialcontent.com/stocks/article/finterra-2026-2-27-the-valuation-reset-a-deep-dive-into-novo-nordisk-nvo-in-2026\"},{\"title\":\"NVO Stock Price Prediction 2026, 2027 & 2030: Analyst Targets & Quantum Computing Outlook • Benzinga\",\"url\":\"https://www.benzinga.com/money/ozempic-novo-nordisk-stock-price-prediction\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Stock Forecast | Guidance Cut and Buyback | Capital.com\",\"url\":\"https://capital.com/en-int/market-updates/novo-nordisk-stock-forecast-13-03-2026\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Stock Forecast | Wegovy HD Launch, 2026 Sales Cut | Capital.com\",\"url\":\"https://capital.com/en-int/market-updates/novo-nordisk-stock-forecast-27-04-2026\"},{\"title\":\"Daily Breeze: Local News, Sports, Things to Do - The Valuation Reset: A Deep-Dive into Novo Nordisk (NVO) in 2026\",\"url\":\"https://markets.financialcontent.com/dailybreeze/article/finterra-2026-2-27-the-valuation-reset-a-deep-dive-into-novo-nordisk-nvo-in-2026\"},{\"title\":\"Ahead of Earnings, Is Novo Stock a Buy, a Sell, or Fairly Valued? | Morningstar\",\"url\":\"https://www.morningstar.com/stocks/ahead-earnings-is-novo-stock-buy-sell-or-fairly-valued\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk sinks 16% after weight loss drug fails to match Eli Lilly's in trial\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/02/23/novo-nordisk-stock-cagrisema-trial-fails-weight-loss.html\"},{\"title\":\"Is Novo Nordisk Stock a Buy After its Collapse? | Morningstar\",\"url\":\"https://www.morningstar.com/stocks/is-novo-nordisk-stock-buy-after-its-collapse\"},{\"title\":\"Drug pricing, patent losses, deals: Novo Nordisk, Pfizer execs weigh in\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/01/20/drug-pricing-patent-losses-deals-novo-nordisk-pfizer.html\"}]\n\nBased on the web search results, here are the key risks facing Novo Nordisk (NVO) for 2025-2026:\n\n## CagriSema Trial Failure\n\nCagriSema, a next-generation dual-agonist expected to be the \"Lilly-killer,\" failed in the Phase 3 REDEFINE 4 trial in February 2026 to show superiority over Lilly's tirzepatide. Patients taking a 2.4 mg dose of CagriSema achieved a weight loss of 23% after 84 weeks compared to 25.5% with a 15 mg dose of tirzepatide. CagriSema could have accounted for between 15% and 25% of Novo's revenue by 2030.\n\n## Medicare Drug Pricing & Trump Agreement\n\nUnder the Inflation Reduction Act (IRA), Ozempic and Wegovy face \"maximum fair prices\" starting January 1, 2027, with prices of $274 and $385 per month, respectively, significantly lower than current net prices. Novo Nordisk secured a three-year Section 232 tariff exemption through its November 2025 agreement with the Trump administration to reduce Ozempic and Wegovy prices.\n\n## Tariffs\n\nThe imposition of U.S. tariffs on European pharmaceutical imports, including key Novo Nordisk drugs like Ozempic and Wegovy, impose a 15% levy, raising drug costs in the crucial U.S. market.\n\n## GLP-1 Competition\n\nAs of early 2026, Eli Lilly's Zepbound and Mounjaro have captured approximately 60% of the U.S. GLP-1 market.\n\n## Guidance & Margin Pressure\n\n2026 Guidance forecasts a sales and operating profit decline of 5% to 13%, marking the company's first projected annual decline since 2017. Gross margins, historically above 80%, are being squeezed by aggressive net pricing discounts in the U.S. and the capital-intensive integration of the Catalent facilities.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"56cadf2b-a7e5-4fc7-9037-6b601a7b78dc","uuid":"9ee8e781-20a7-4a89-9b81-3cd575fd207e","timestamp":"2026-04-28T16:54:56.706Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk NVO risks 2025 2026 CagriSema failure tariffs Medicare drug pricing compounding GLP-1","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01Tn9okX85GDt7ZzqRJE8gVp","content":[{"title":"The Valuation Reset: A Deep-Dive into Novo Nordisk (NVO) in 2026","url":"https://markets.financialcontent.com/wral/article/finterra-2026-2-27-the-valuation-reset-a-deep-dive-into-novo-nordisk-nvo-in-2026"},{"title":"FinancialContent - The Valuation Reset: A Deep-Dive into Novo Nordisk (NVO) in 2026","url":"https://markets.financialcontent.com/stocks/article/finterra-2026-2-27-the-valuation-reset-a-deep-dive-into-novo-nordisk-nvo-in-2026"},{"title":"NVO Stock Price Prediction 2026, 2027 & 2030: Analyst Targets & Quantum Computing Outlook • Benzinga","url":"https://www.benzinga.com/money/ozempic-novo-nordisk-stock-price-prediction"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Stock Forecast | Guidance Cut and Buyback | Capital.com","url":"https://capital.com/en-int/market-updates/novo-nordisk-stock-forecast-13-03-2026"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Stock Forecast | Wegovy HD Launch, 2026 Sales Cut | Capital.com","url":"https://capital.com/en-int/market-updates/novo-nordisk-stock-forecast-27-04-2026"},{"title":"Daily Breeze: Local News, Sports, Things to Do - The Valuation Reset: A Deep-Dive into Novo Nordisk (NVO) in 2026","url":"https://markets.financialcontent.com/dailybreeze/article/finterra-2026-2-27-the-valuation-reset-a-deep-dive-into-novo-nordisk-nvo-in-2026"},{"title":"Ahead of Earnings, Is Novo Stock a Buy, a Sell, or Fairly Valued? | Morningstar","url":"https://www.morningstar.com/stocks/ahead-earnings-is-novo-stock-buy-sell-or-fairly-valued"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk sinks 16% after weight loss drug fails to match Eli Lilly's in trial","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/02/23/novo-nordisk-stock-cagrisema-trial-fails-weight-loss.html"},{"title":"Is Novo Nordisk Stock a Buy After its Collapse? | Morningstar","url":"https://www.morningstar.com/stocks/is-novo-nordisk-stock-buy-after-its-collapse"},{"title":"Drug pricing, patent losses, deals: Novo Nordisk, Pfizer execs weigh in","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/01/20/drug-pricing-patent-losses-deals-novo-nordisk-pfizer.html"}]},"Based on the web search results, here are the key risks facing Novo Nordisk (NVO) for 2025-2026:\n\n## CagriSema Trial Failure\n\nCagriSema, a next-generation dual-agonist expected to be the \"Lilly-killer,\" failed in the Phase 3 REDEFINE 4 trial in February 2026 to show superiority over Lilly's tirzepatide. Patients taking a 2.4 mg dose of CagriSema achieved a weight loss of 23% after 84 weeks compared to 25.5% with a 15 mg dose of tirzepatide. CagriSema could have accounted for between 15% and 25% of Novo's revenue by 2030.\n\n## Medicare Drug Pricing & Trump Agreement\n\nUnder the Inflation Reduction Act (IRA), Ozempic and Wegovy face \"maximum fair prices\" starting January 1, 2027, with prices of $274 and $385 per month, respectively, significantly lower than current net prices. Novo Nordisk secured a three-year Section 232 tariff exemption through its November 2025 agreement with the Trump administration to reduce Ozempic and Wegovy prices.\n\n## Tariffs\n\nThe imposition of U.S. tariffs on European pharmaceutical imports, including key Novo Nordisk drugs like Ozempic and Wegovy, impose a 15% levy, raising drug costs in the crucial U.S. market.\n\n## GLP-1 Competition\n\nAs of early 2026, Eli Lilly's Zepbound and Mounjaro have captured approximately 60% of the U.S. GLP-1 market.\n\n## Guidance & Margin Pressure\n\n2026 Guidance forecasts a sales and operating profit decline of 5% to 13%, marking the company's first projected annual decline since 2017. Gross margins, historically above 80%, are being squeezed by aggressive net pricing discounts in the U.S. and the capital-intensive integration of the Catalent facilities."],"durationSeconds":8.656788291000005}}
