{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01D2hFSvYvmnSaUfBtYDu6eN","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk FY2025 full year results February 2026 Ozempic Wegovy revenue USD breakdown Q4\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Financial results and events overview - Novo Nordisk\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/investors/financial-results.html\"},{\"title\":\"Financial performance - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/strategic-aspirations/financial-performance.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Q3 2025 Earnings Transcript | The Motley Fool\",\"url\":\"https://www.fool.com/earnings/call-transcripts/2025/12/11/novo-nordisk-nvo-q3-2025-earnings-transcript/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk – a focused healthcare company Investor presentation\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/pdfs/financial-results/2026/Q4-2025-investor-presentation-4Feb.pdf\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk shares tumble after company warns of sales hit this year\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/02/03/novo-nordisk-2025-earnings-wegovy-ozempic.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025 (PDF)\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/irmaterial/annual_report/2026/novo-nordisk-annual-report-2025.pdf\"},{\"title\":\"Financial report for the period 1 January 2025 to 30 September 2025\",\"url\":\"https://ml-eu.globenewswire.com/Resource/Download/ae93d17e-6c68-433e-ac46-9ea814575af0\"},{\"title\":\"Financials - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2024\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2024/strategic-aspirations/financials.html\"},{\"title\":\"Wegovy, Ozempic maker Novo Nordisk Q3 earnings; shares fall\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2025/11/05/wegovy-ozempic-maker-novo-nordisk-q3-earnings.html\"},{\"title\":\"UPDATE: Novo shares plummet on sales, profit warning for '26 as 2 top execs head for the door\",\"url\":\"https://www.fiercepharma.com/pharma/novo-shares-plummet-sales-profit-warning-26\"}]\n\nBased on Novo Nordisk's FY2025 full-year results released in early February 2026, here are the key findings:\n\n## Full-Year 2025 Results\n\nOzempic generated roughly 127 billion kroner ($20 billion) for the year, while Wegovy took home 79.1 billion kroner (nearly $13 billion).\n\n## Q4 2025 Results (Fourth Quarter)\n\nIn the fourth quarter, Novo net sales amounted to 79.1 billion Danish kroner ($12.5 billion), slightly ahead of analysts' expectations of 77.8 billion kroner.\n\nSpecifically for the quarter:\n- Ozempic brought in 31.8 billion kroner in the quarter, up 1% from the same period last year at constant exchange rates\n- Wegovy sales were 21.9 billion kroner, up 17%\n\n## 2026 Outlook\n\nFor 2026, the drugmaker sees sales and operating profit both declining between 5% and 13% at constant exchange rates.\n\nThe results highlight the contrasting fortunes of Novo Nordisk's flagship products, with Ozempic showing stagnant growth amid pricing pressures, while Wegovy continues to demonstrate stronger momentum despite the challenging market environment.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"56cadf2b-a7e5-4fc7-9037-6b601a7b78dc","uuid":"39063bf7-08bc-4981-9fc6-6385fc34a25b","timestamp":"2026-04-28T16:55:07.256Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk FY2025 full year results February 2026 Ozempic Wegovy revenue USD breakdown Q4","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_017fpTqZSJfeuRmYDBdFGWKN","content":[{"title":"Financial results and events overview - Novo Nordisk","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/investors/financial-results.html"},{"title":"Financial performance - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025","url":"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/strategic-aspirations/financial-performance.html"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Q3 2025 Earnings Transcript | Th