onstant exchange rates\n- Wegovy sales were 21.9 billion kroner, up 17%\n\n## 2026 Outlook\n\nFor 2026, the drugmaker sees sales and operating profit both declining between 5% and 13% at constant exchange rates.\n\nThe results highlight the contrasting fortunes of Novo Nordisk's flagship products, with Ozempic showing stagnant growth amid pricing pressures, while Wegovy continues to demonstrate stronger momentum despite the challenging market environment."],"durationSeconds":5.016295958999995}}
