{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0153hagzNgYzTfqWH215dnjY","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk NVO insider ownership Novo Holdings foundation institutional ownership 2025\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk AS (NVO) Stock Holders - Institutional & Insider Ownership | GuruFocus\",\"url\":\"https://www.gurufocus.com/stock/NVO/ownership\"},{\"title\":\"NVO - Novo Nordisk A/S - Depositary Receipt (Common Stock) Stock - Stock Price, Institutional Ownership, Shareholders (NYSE)\",\"url\":\"https://fintel.io/so/us/nvo\"},{\"title\":\"Share and ownership structure of Novo Nordisk\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/investors/stock-information/share-and-ownership-structure.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Institutional Ownership 2026 $NVO\",\"url\":\"https://www.marketbeat.com/stocks/NYSE/NVO/institutional-ownership/\"},{\"title\":\"Who owns Novo Nordisk? NVO Stock Ownership - TipRanks.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.tipranks.com/stocks/nvo/ownership\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S Common Stock (NVO) Holding Activity, Ownership Summary, & Shareholders | Nasdaq\",\"url\":\"https://www.nasdaq.com/market-activity/stocks/nvo/institutional-holdings\"},{\"title\":\"NVO 13F Hedge Fund & Institutional Ownership | HedgeFollow\",\"url\":\"https://hedgefollow.com/stocks/NVO\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (ADR) Ownership Pattern for Apr-2025 - Insider, Institutional, Mutual Fund shareholdings\",\"url\":\"https://us.trendlyne.com/us/equity/ownership/1404346/NVO/apr-2025/novo-nordisk-adr/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Insider Ownership & Holdings - Yahoo Finance\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NVO/insider-roster/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Ownership | Who Owns Novo Nordisk?\",\"url\":\"https://www.tickergate.com/stocks/nvo/ownership\"}]\n\nBased on the web search results, here's what I found regarding Novo Nordisk's ownership structure:\n\n## Novo Holdings and Foundation Ownership\n\nNovo Nordisk's A shares are not listed and are held by Novo Holdings A/S, a Danish public limited liability company wholly owned by the Novo Nordisk Foundation. The Foundation has a dual objective: to provide a stable basis for the commercial and research activities conducted by the companies within the Novo Group (of which Novo Nordisk is the largest), and to support scientific and humanitarian purposes. Additionally, according to the Articles of Association of the Foundation, the A shares cannot be divested.\n\n## Institutional and Insider Ownership\n\nAccording to the ownership data from October 2025, Novo Nordisk is owned by 7.09% institutional investors, 0.01% insiders, and 92.91% retail investors. Jennison associates is the largest institutional shareholder, holding 0.42% of NVO shares.\n\nIt's worth noting that the ownership percentages vary slightly depending on the data source and timing, but the overall picture shows that while Novo Holdings/Novo Nordisk Foundation maintains significant voting control through the A shares, institutional ownership of the publicly traded shares remains relatively limited.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"56cadf2b-a7e5-4fc7-9037-6b601a7b78dc","uuid":"3ebcbf52-5a68-4e65-882c-b7deb63bfea2","timestamp":"2026-04-28T16:55:18.969Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk NVO insider ownership Novo Holdings foundation institutional ownership 2025","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_0134zHFZpoKCEdFa9nuMeoC1","content":[{"title":"Novo Nordisk AS (NVO) Stock Holders - Institutional & Insider Ownership | GuruFocus","url":"https://www.gurufocus.com/stock/NVO/ownership"},{"title":"NVO - Novo Nordisk A/S - Depositary Receipt (Common Stock) Stock - Stock Price, Institutional Ownership, Shareholders (NYSE)","url":"https://fintel.io/so/us/nvo"},{"title":"Share and ownership structure of Novo Nordisk","url":"https:/