{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HbZ8fDWCKButPyksFUdCo9","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk business overview segments Ozempic Wegovy semaglutide revenue breakdown 2025\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Top Selling Products 2025\",\"url\":\"https://www.accio.com/business/novo-nordisk-top-selling-products\"},{\"title\":\"Slowing Ozempic, Wegovy sales lead to cut in top end of ...\",\"url\":\"https://firstwordpharma.com/story/6516083\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk predicts milder growth in 2025 after obesity star Wegovy doubles sales in Q4 | Fierce Pharma\",\"url\":\"https://www.fiercepharma.com/pharma/novo-nordisk-predicts-milder-sales-growth-2025-after-obesity-star-wegovy-doubles-numbers-q4\"},{\"title\":\"Novo cuts GLP-1 prices 70%, but semaglutide revenue could grow in 2026\",\"url\":\"https://www.drugdiscoverytrends.com/novo-slashes-us-glp-1-prices-by-up-to-70-but-2026-semaglutide-revenue-could-hold-steady-or-even-grow/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo's 2025 Revenue Reaches USD 46.9b as Semaglutide Hits USD 34.6b\",\"url\":\"https://global.pharmcube.com/news/detail/940e06b555214f078e49a22d27639d13?type=dailyNews\"},{\"title\":\"Ozempic and Wegovy pumped $26 billion into Novo Nordisk last year. Can the pharma giant find its next breakthrough before the boom ends? | Fortune\",\"url\":\"https://fortune.com/2025/03/31/ozempic-wegovy-novo-nordisk-nvidia/\"},{\"title\":\"The Heavy Price of GLP-1 Drugs: How Financialization Drives Pharmaceutical Patent Abuse and Health Inequities for GLP-1 Therapies\",\"url\":\"https://www.i-mak.org/glp-1/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Semaglutide Revenue: How Ozempic and Wegovy Are Driving Record Profits - Pharmacy Business Hub\",\"url\":\"https://pharmabusinesshub.com/novo-nordisk-semaglutide-revenue/\"},{\"title\":\"Financial performance - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/strategic-aspirations/financial-performance.html\"},{\"title\":\"Q3-investor-presentation-2025.pdf\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/pdfs/financial-results/2025/Q3-investor-presentation-2025.pdf\"}]\n\nBased on the web search results, here's a comprehensive overview of Novo Nordisk's business segments, focusing on their semaglutide-based products:\n\n## Business Overview\n\nNovo Nordisk is a leading global healthcare company, founded in 1923 and headquartered in Denmark, with a purpose to drive change to defeat diabetes and other serious chronic diseases.\n\n## Business Segments\n\nThe diabetes and obesity care segments account for 94% of total sales, generating combined revenue of about USD 43.9 billion in 2025.\n\n## Semaglutide Products & Revenue Breakdown\n\nNovo Nordisk's business is dominated by three semaglutide-based products:\n\n**Product Lineup:**\n- Ozempic (injection for diabetes, approved in 2017), Rybelsus (oral tablet for diabetes, approved in 2019), and Wegovy (injection for weight loss, approved in 2021)\n\n**2025 Revenue Performance:**\nNovo Nordisk announced 2025 total revenue of DKK 309.1 billion (approximately USD 46.8 billion), representing 10% growth at constant exchange rates.\n\nSales of the company's GLP-1-based medicines, led by the semaglutide products Ozempic, Rybelsus and Wegovy, reached DKK 234.5 billion (USD 35.6 billion), with the three semaglutide products collectively generating USD 34.6 billion in sales.\n\n**Individual Product Breakdown (2025):**\n- Ozempic sales increased by 6% measured in Danish kroner and by 10% at constant exchange rates (CER) to DKK 127,089 million\n- Rybelsus sales decreased by 5% measured in Danish kroner and by 2% at CER to DKK 22,093 million\n\n## Market Position\n\nWhile Novo Nordisk's global market share in GLP-1 diabetes drugs declined to 45.8% amid competitive pressure, it maintained a dominant 83.1% share of the Chinese GLP-1 market for diabetes.\n\n## 2026 Outlook\n\nFor 2026, Novo Nordisk forecasts a sales decline of 5% to 13% at constant exchange rates, reflecting expected pricing pressures and market dynamics.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"63953807-54da-4e4a-a0f9-cb4a0b97eca8","uuid":"7fa28fa3-e6b7-4392-93b4-23673fcc2cc6","timestamp":"2026-04-28T17:04:56.069Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk business overview segments Ozempic Wegovy semaglutide revenue breakdown 2025","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01G5q2HYdbuyccY6eAmukZcU","content":[{"title":"Novo Nordisk Top Selling Products 2025","url":"https://www.accio.com/business/novo-nordisk-top-selling-products"},{"title":"Slowing Ozempic, Wegovy sales lead to cut in top end of ...","url":"https://firstwordpharma.com/story/6516083"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk predicts milder growth in 2025 after obesity star Wegovy doubles sales in Q4 | Fierce Pharma","url":"https://www.fiercepharma.com/pharma/novo-nordisk-predicts-milder-sales-growth-2025-after-obesity-star-wegovy-doubles-numbers-q4"},{"title":"Novo cuts GLP-1 prices 70%, but semaglutide revenue could grow in 2026","url":"https://www.drugdiscoverytrends.com/novo-slashes-us-glp-1-prices-by-up-to-70-but-2026-semaglutide-revenue-could-hold-steady-or-even-grow/"},{"title":"Novo's 2025 Revenue Reaches USD 46.9b as Semaglutide Hits USD 34.6b","url":"https://global.pharmcube.com/news/detail/940e06b555214f078e49a22d27639d13?type=dailyNews"},{"title":"Ozempic and Wegovy pumped $26 billion into Novo Nordisk last year. Can the pharma giant find its next breakthrough before the boom ends? | Fortune","url":"https://fortune.com/2025/03/31/ozempic-wegovy-novo-nordisk-nvidia/"},{"title":"The Heavy Price of GLP-1 Drugs: How Financialization Drives Pharmaceutical Patent Abuse and Health Inequities for GLP-1 Therapies","url":"https://www.i-mak.org/glp-1/"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Semaglutide Revenue: How Ozempic and Wegovy Are Driving Record Pro