{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01B46WNibFcfvMqmAEXmBVBm","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk NVO balance sheet total assets debt equity cash 2023 2024 2025\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Balance Sheet & Financial Health Metrics - Simply Wall St\",\"url\":\"https://simplywall.st/stocks/us/pharmaceuticals-biotech/nyse-nvo/novo-nordisk/health\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Balance Sheet - Yahoo Finance\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NVO/balance-sheet/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Balance Sheet\",\"url\":\"https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/nvo/financials/balance-sheet/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk ADR (NVO) Balance Sheet - Investing.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.investing.com/equities/novo-nordis-balance-sheet\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Total Assets 2012-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends\",\"url\":\"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/total-assets\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/investors/annual-report.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Balance Sheet 2011-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends\",\"url\":\"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/balance-sheet\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Stock Financials: Balance Sheet | Seeking Alpha\",\"url\":\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVO/balance-sheet\"},{\"title\":\"FORM 20-F 2024 - Annual Report 2025 - Novo Nordisk\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2024/_assets/downloads/novo-nordisk-form-20-f-2024.pdf\"},{\"title\":\"Financials - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2024\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2024/strategic-aspirations/financials.html\"}]\n\nBased on the web search results, here's information on Novo Nordisk's balance sheet metrics:\n\n## Total Assets\nNovo Nordisk total assets for 2024 were $67.54B, a 47.91% increase from 2023. Novo Nordisk total assets for 2023 were $45.663B, a 33.67% increase from 2022. Novo Nordisk total assets for the quarter ending September 30, 2025 were $80.224B, a 36.94% increase year-over-year.\n\n## Debt and Equity\nNovo Nordisk has a total shareholder equity of DKK194.0B and total debt of DKK122.4B, which brings its debt-to-equity ratio to 63.1%.\n\n## Cash\nIn its most recent quarterly filing, Novo Nordisk ADR reported 26,464.00 Million DKK in cash and cash equivalents.\n\n## Liabilities\nIts total assets and total liabilities are DKK542.9B and DKK348.9B respectively.\n\nThe data shows significant growth in total assets from 2023 through 2025, with the company maintaining a substantial balance sheet base supported by equity financing and debt funding, including recent acquisitions like the Catalent manufacturing sites acquisition.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"63953807-54da-4e4a-a0f9-cb4a0b97eca8","uuid":"787c9c92-a06e-462e-a645-8e6b9e9c862d","timestamp":"2026-04-28T17:05:21.291Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk NVO balance sheet total assets debt equity cash 2023 2024 2025","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01BgUzb6QS6wVkVk1RPp863f","content":[{"title":"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Balance Sheet & Financial Health Metrics - Simply Wall St","url":"https://simplywall.st/stocks/us/pharmaceuticals-biotech/nyse-nvo/novo-nordisk/health"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Balance Sheet - Yahoo Finance","url":"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NVO/balance-sheet/"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Balance Sheet","url":"https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/nvo/financials/balance-sheet/"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk ADR (NVO) Balance Sheet - Investing.com","url":"https://www.investing.com/equities/novo-nordis-balance-sheet"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Total Assets 2012-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends","url":"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/total-assets"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025","url":"https://