{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01F1E6F76FUJNeBk7Mhw6paD","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk NVO risks 2026 oral semaglutide Ozempic patent IRA Medicare pricing GLP-1 competition\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk enters 2026 on the defense as it faces a ‘must-win’ battle in the U.S. market\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/01/01/novo-nordisk-faces-must-win-battle-over-us-wegovy-ozempic-in-2026.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Product Patents | Novo Nordisk U.S.\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk-us.com/products/product-patents.html\"},{\"title\":\"The Heavy Price of GLP-1 Drugs: How Financialization Drives Pharmaceutical Patent Abuse and Health Inequities for GLP-1 Therapies\",\"url\":\"https://www.i-mak.org/glp-1/\"},{\"title\":\"The Battle for Billions: Understanding the Ozempic Patent ...\",\"url\":\"https://journals.library.columbia.edu/index.php/stlr/blog/view/653\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk’s China Patent Pause and Washington Pivot Create a Split-Screen Reality - Stocks Today\",\"url\":\"https://stockstoday.com/novo-nordisks-china-patent-pause-and-washington-pivot-create-a-split-screen-reality/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Downgrade: Semaglutide Patent Risks in 2026\",\"url\":\"https://capwolf.com/novo-nordisk-downgrade-semaglutide-patent-risks-in-2026/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Faces Pricing Pressure and Patent Expiry Risks\",\"url\":\"https://www.gurufocus.com/news/8587173/novo-nordisk-nvo-faces-pricing-pressure-and-patent-expiry-risks\"},{\"title\":\"Overpatented, Overpriced 2025: A Data Brief on Medicare-Negotiated Drugs: Eliquis, Ozempic, Rybelsus and Wegovy\",\"url\":\"https://www.i-mak.org/overpatented/\"},{\"title\":\"Semaglutide (Ozempic) Market: Navigating The Patent Cliff And Strategic Implications\",\"url\":\"https://www.grandviewresearch.com/market-trends/semaglutide-market-navigating-patent-cliff-strategic-implications\"},{\"title\":\"The Valuation Reset: A Deep-Dive into Novo Nordisk (NVO) in 2026\",\"url\":\"https://markets.financialcontent.com/wral/article/finterra-2026-2-27-the-valuation-reset-a-deep-dive-into-novo-nordisk-nvo-in-2026\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's a comprehensive overview of Novo Nordisk's key risks and challenges in 2026 related to oral semaglutide, Ozempic patent issues, Medicare pricing, and GLP-1 competition:\n\n## Medicare Pricing and IRA Impact\n\nThe U.S. government has selected semaglutide for Medicare price negotiation under the Inflation Reduction Act, with Ozempic capped at $274 per month starting in 2027 (down from a list price of $959) and higher doses of Wegovy at $385 monthly. Novo Nordisk has sued to block the policy, so far without success.\n\n## Patent Landscape\n\nThe patent situation is complex. The main compound patent protecting semaglutide should technically expire in March 2026, but has been extended by over five years as a result of Patent Term Adjustment (PTA) and Patent Term Extension (PTE). However, Novo's patent in China is set to expire in 2026, which means generic competition could make China the largest market for semaglutide medications.\n\n## International Patent Expirations and Market Risks\n\nLower pricing as a result of MFN (Most Favored Nation pricing), as well as patent expiries in jurisdictions including Brazil, Canada and China will \"probably lead to a decreasing top line\". In 2026-2027, revenue loss is expected to be more pronounced, with localized patent expirations in key emerging markets such as China, Brazil, India, and Canada projected to result in a 5-8% share loss.\n\n## GLP-1 Competition\n\nCompetition is likely to intensify beyond Lilly and compounders, as several drugmakers — including Pfizer, Amgen, AstraZeneca, Roche — advance late-stage candidates through their pipelines. Eli Lilly's Tirzepatide (Mounjaro) has emerged as a formidable competitor, surpassing Wegovy in several regions due to strategic collaborations.\n\n## Oral Semaglutide Progress\n\nOral Wegovy successfully launched in 2025, offering a needle-free option for patients, though oral Wegovy outsells Lilly's pill 5-to-1.\n\n## Pipeline Challenges\n\nCagriSema, the next-generation dual-agonist, had a Phase 3 trial in February 2026 that failed to show superiority over Lilly's tirzepatide.\n\n## Overall Financial Outlook\n\nManagement has guided for a 5% to 13% decline in both adjusted revenue and profit for 2026, driven by U.S. pricing pressure and patent expirations in select markets.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"63953807-54da-4e4a-a0f9-cb4a0b97eca8","uuid":"7c4f60c4-5c1b-424f-8f81-ba6496a53a1a","timestamp":"2026-04-28T17:06:10.026Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk NVO risks 2026 oral semaglutide Ozempic patent IRA Medicare pricing GLP-1 competition","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_016X6PA1i2YrgRaN1sxU9wVX","content":[{"title":"Novo Nordisk enters 2026 on the defense as it faces a ‘must-win’ battle in the U.S. market","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/01/01/novo-nordisk-faces-must-win-battle-over-us-wegovy-ozempic-in-2026.html"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Product Patents | Novo Nordisk U.S.","url":"https://www.novonordisk-us.com/products/product-patents.html"},{"title":"The Heavy Price of GLP-1 Drugs: How Financialization Drives Pharmaceutical Patent Abuse and Health Inequities for GLP-1 Therapies","url":"https://www.i-mak.org/glp-1/"},{"title":"The Battle for Billions: Understanding the Ozempic Patent ...","url":"https://journals.library.columbia.edu/index.php/stlr/blog/view/653"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk’s China Patent Pause and Washington Pivot Create a Split-Screen Reality - Stocks Today","url":"https://stockstoday.com/novo-nordisks-china-patent-pause-and-washington-pivot-create-a-split-screen-reality/"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Downgrade: Semaglutide Patent Risks in 2026","url":"https://ca