{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01UgL8nHmsuMMK93hkUon1Le","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk NVO return on equity ROE ROA ROIC 2021 2022 2023 2024 2025\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk ROE - Return on Equity 2012-2025 | NVO\",\"url\":\"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/roe\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Return on Equity (ROE) - Current & Historical Data (Apr 2026)\",\"url\":\"https://www.financecharts.com/stocks/NVO/growth/roe\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Return on Investment 2012-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends\",\"url\":\"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/roi\"},{\"title\":\"NVO (Novo Nordisk A/S) ROIC %\",\"url\":\"https://www.gurufocus.com/term/roic/NYSE:NVO\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Average ROE\",\"url\":\"https://www.wisesheets.io/roe/NVO\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NYSE:NVO) Return on Common Equity - Investing.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.investing.com/pro/NYSE:NVO/explorer/roe\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S ROIC | NOV.DE\",\"url\":\"https://mlq.ai/stocks/NOV.DE/roic/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Financial Ratios\",\"url\":\"https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/nvo/financials/ratios/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NYSE:NVO) - Earnings & Revenue Performance - Simply Wall St\",\"url\":\"https://simplywall.st/stocks/us/pharmaceuticals-biotech/nyse-nvo/novo-nordisk/past\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Stock Analysis & Key Metrics | KoalaGains\",\"url\":\"https://koalagains.com/stocks/NYSE/NVO\"}]\n\nBased on the web search results, here's the information on Novo Nordisk's (NVO) return metrics for 2021-2025:\n\n## Return on Equity (ROE)\n\nNovo Nordisk's return on common equity increased in 2021 (71.2%, +2.2%), 2022 (72.0%, +1.1%), and 2023 (88.1%, +22.3%), and decreased in 2024 (80.8%, -8.3%) and 2025 (60.7%, -24.9%).\n\n## Return on Assets (ROA)\n\nThe company's Return on Assets (ROA) stands at 18.87% (current trailing twelve-month basis).\n\n## Return on Invested Capital (ROIC)\n\nFor the fiscal year 2024, Novo Nordisk's Return on Invested Capital (ROIC) was 46.03%. More recently, Novo Nordisk A/S currently shows a trailing twelve-month (TTM) Return on Invested Capital (ROIC) of 29.53%.\n\n## Summary\n\nNovo Nordisk demonstrated strong profitability metrics across 2021-2024, with ROE peaking at 88.1% in 2023 before declining in 2024-2025. The company's ROIC metrics (46.03% for fiscal 2024 and 29.53% TTM) indicate exceptional capital efficiency, well above typical industry benchmarks.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"63953807-54da-4e4a-a0f9-cb4a0b97eca8","uuid":"c6b9d62e-a2f4-45b0-ba6f-d3dcc3fd9177","timestamp":"2026-04-28T17:06:27.002Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk NVO return on equity ROE ROA ROIC 2021 2022 2023 2024 2025","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_017qkfBnhyxi8wh7wkgCNQSe","content":[{"title":"Novo Nordisk ROE - Return on Equity 2012-2025 | NVO","url":"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/roe"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Return on Equity (ROE) - Current & Historical Data (Apr 2026)","url":"https://www.financecharts.com/stocks/NVO/growth/roe"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Return on Investment 2012-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends","url":"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/roi"},{"title":"NVO (Novo Nordisk A/S) ROIC %","url":"https://www.gurufocus.com/term/roic/NYSE:NVO"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Average ROE","url":"https://www.wisesheets.io/roe/NVO"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S (NYSE:NVO) Return on Common Equity - Investing.com","url":"https://www.investing.com/pro/NYSE:NVO/explorer/roe"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S ROIC | NOV.DE","url":"https://mlq.ai/stocks/NOV.DE/roic/"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Financial Ratios","url":"https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/nvo/financials/ratios/"},