{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01LuokZ8kuNaxXqwyFXYCHpC","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk NVO segment revenue breakdown GLP-1 Ozempic Wegovy 2024 2025 annual report\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Financials - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2024\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2024/strategic-aspirations/financials.html\"},{\"title\":\"Financial performance - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/strategic-aspirations/financial-performance.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk – a focused healthcare company Investor presentation\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/pdfs/financial-results/2025/Q2-2025-investor-presentation-updated.pdf\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Q3 2025 Earnings Transcript | The Motley Fool\",\"url\":\"https://www.fool.com/earnings/call-transcripts/2025/12/11/novo-nordisk-nvo-q3-2025-earnings-transcript/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Q3 Earnings & Revenues Miss, GLP-1 Drugs Face US Hurdles\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/novo-nordisk-q3-earnings-revenues-153000106.html\"},{\"title\":\"Ozempic and Wegovy pumped $26 billion into Novo Nordisk last year. Can the pharma giant find its next breakthrough before the boom ends? | Fortune\",\"url\":\"https://fortune.com/2025/03/31/ozempic-wegovy-novo-nordisk-nvidia/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo narrows sales outlook as GLP-1 price cuts loom | BioPharma Dive\",\"url\":\"https://www.biopharmadive.com/news/novo-nordisk-3q-earnings-obesity-drug-sales-outlook/804727/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk predicts milder growth in 2025 after obesity star Wegovy doubles sales in Q4 | Fierce Pharma\",\"url\":\"https://www.fiercepharma.com/pharma/novo-nordisk-predicts-milder-sales-growth-2025-after-obesity-star-wegovy-doubles-numbers-q4\"},{\"title\":\"Financial report for the period 1 January 2025 to 30 September 2025\",\"url\":\"https://ml-eu.globenewswire.com/Resource/Download/ae93d17e-6c68-433e-ac46-9ea814575af0\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk details 2025 results and GLP‑1 growth | NVO SEC Filing - Form 20-F\",\"url\":\"https://www.stocktitan.net/sec-filings/NVO/20-f-novo-nordisk-a-s-files-annual-report-foreign-issuer-3e3a4c2d4e89.html\"}]\n\nBased on the web search results, here is a comprehensive breakdown of Novo Nordisk's segment revenue for GLP-1 products:\n\n## 2024 Annual Results\n\n**Obesity Care (Wegovy & Saxenda):**\nSales of obesity care products increased by 56-57% at constant exchange rates to DKK 65,146 million. More specifically, Wegovy sales for all of 2024 totaled 58.2 billion kroner (around $8 billion), compared to 31.3 billion kroner the prior year.\n\n**Diabetes Care (GLP-1 Products):**\nSales in Diabetes care increased by 19-20% at constant exchange rates to DKK 206,618 million driven by growth of GLP-1-based products and insulins. Within this segment, GLP-1-based products for type 2 diabetes (Rybelsus, Ozempic and Victoza) increased by 21-22% at constant exchange rates to DKK 149,125 million.\n\n**Ozempic Specifically:**\nOzempic sales increased by 26% to DKK 120,342 million, with Ozempic bringing home around 120 billion kroner (nearly $17 billion) over the same stretch.\n\n## 2025 Full Year Results\n\nWegovy sales reached DKK 79,106 million and Ozempic DKK 127,089 million in 2025, with obesity products Saxenda and Wegovy generating DKK 82,347 million in total.\n\nGLP-1-based products for type 2 diabetes increased by 2-6% at constant exchange rates to DKK 152,202 million.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c2f9e2bf-4eb3-44bc-922b-8db97158fefa","uuid":"14e391e3-4116-4fa0-a4f4-45b286005497","timestamp":"2026-04-28T22:24:18.922Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk NVO segment revenue breakdown GLP-1 Ozempic Wegovy 2024 2025 annual report","results":[{"tool_use_id":"