{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_012NoVmACQuPTJ77MryYUB1z","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk NVO analyst price target consensus Buy Hold Sell 2026\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Stock Forecast: Analyst Ratings, Predictions & Price Target 2026\",\"url\":\"https://public.com/stocks/nvo/forecast-price-target\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Stock Forecast and Price Target 2026 $NVO\",\"url\":\"https://www.marketbeat.com/stocks/NYSE/NVO/forecast/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Stock Forecast & Analyst Price Targets\",\"url\":\"https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/nvo/forecast/\"},{\"title\":\"NVO Stock Price Prediction 2026, 2027 & 2030: Analyst Targets & Quantum Computing Outlook • Benzinga\",\"url\":\"https://www.benzinga.com/money/ozempic-novo-nordisk-stock-price-prediction\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk ADR (NVO) Stock Forecast & Price Target - Investing.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.investing.com/equities/novo-nordis-consensus-estimates\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Stock Forecast, Price Targets and Analysts Predictions - TipRanks.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.tipranks.com/stocks/nvo/forecast\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S: Target Price Consensus and Analysts Recommendations | NOVO B | DK0062498333 | MarketScreener\",\"url\":\"https://www.marketscreener.com/quote/stock/NOVO-NORDISK-A-S-1412980/consensus/\"},{\"title\":\"What is the current Price Target and Forecast for Novo Nordisk (NVO)\",\"url\":\"https://www.zacks.com/stock/research/NVO/price-target-stock-forecast\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Analyst Ratings and Price Targets | NYSE:NVO | Benzinga\",\"url\":\"https://www.benzinga.com/quote/NVO/analyst-ratings\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Stock Forecast 2026–2030 | Future Outlook | Capital.com\",\"url\":\"https://capital.com/en-int/analysis/novo-nordisk-stock-forecast\"}]\n\nBased on the search results for Novo Nordisk (NVO) analyst ratings and price targets in 2026, here's what I found:\n\n## Analyst Consensus Rating\n\nAccording to 6 analysts, Novo Nordisk (NVO) has a Buy consensus rating as of Apr 25, 2026. However, other sources show mixed results: 4 analysts have a consensus rating of \"Hold\" and an average price target of $51, while TipRanks reports a consensus rating of Hold based on 1 buy rating, 7 hold ratings and 0 sell ratings.\n\n33% of analysts recommend a Strong Buy, 17% recommend Buy, 33% suggest Holding, 17% advise Selling, and 0% predict a Strong Sell.\n\n## Price Target Consensus\n\nThe analyst price targets vary considerably across different sources:\n\n- 16 analysts give it a consensus price target of $85.31 with the highest target at $160 by Cantor Fitzgerald and the lowest at $41 from Goldman Sachs.\n- According to projections from 12 analysts, the average 12-month price target for Novo Nordisk ADR is 46.63 USD, with a high estimate of 65.83 USD and a low estimate of 36.05 USD.\n- TipRanks shows a consensus rating of Hold with an average price target for Novo Nordisk of 43.00.\n\nThe wide variance in price targets reflects mixed sentiment among analysts regarding the company's growth prospects and risks.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c2f9e2bf-4eb3-44bc-922b-8db97158fefa","uuid":"8ca0ec5b-dd86-4339-bcdc-ad42f6ad40fa","timestamp":"2026-04-28T22:24:31.980Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk NVO analyst price target consensus Buy Hold Sell 2026","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01LvVhFLJA3MJTUFkD9trW99","content":[{"title":"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Stock Forecast: Analyst Ratings, Predictions & Price Target 2026","url":"https://public.com/stocks/nvo/forecast-price-target"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Stock Forecast and Price Target 2026 $NVO","url":"https://www.marketbeat.com/stocks/NYSE/NVO/forecast/"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Stock Forecast & Analyst Price Targets","url"