he segment performance, particularly the Diabetes Care division which appears to be a major revenue driver.\n\nI'm noticing a discrepancy in my revenue calculations when converting the DKK figures to USD. The Diabetes Care and Obesity Care segments in DKK don't seem to be adding up to the total revenue I calculated earlier, so I need to account for other operating segments and income sources to reconcile the numbers. I'm realizing these product revenues are components within the broader diabetes and obesity segments, not standalone figures. Let me search for the actual segment breakdowns to get a clearer picture of how Novo Nordisk's revenue is structured.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":951,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2120,"cache_read_input_tokens":63951,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2120},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c2f9e2bf-4eb3-44bc-922b-8db97158fefa","uuid":"3ebaccf7-55aa-4ad8-9ab2-56b4ee93b81a"}
