sults/2025/Q3-investor-presentation-2025.pdf\"}]\n\nBased on the web search results, here are Novo Nordisk's 2025 full year results for the key segments:\n\n## Full Year 2025 Revenue by Segment (in DKK):\n\n**Obesity Care:**\nSales increased by 26% in Danish kroner and by 31% at CER to DKK 82,347 million.\n\n**Diabetes Care:**\nSales in Diabetes care remained unchanged in Danish kroner and increased by 4% at CER.\n\n**Rare Disease:**\nRare disease sales increased by 5% in Danish kroner and by 9% at CER to DKK 19,608 million.\n\n## Additional Details:\n\nWithin Diabetes care, insulin sales decreased by 4% in Danish kroner and by 1% at CER to DKK 53,137 million. Additionally, Victoza® sales decreased by 45% in Danish kroner and by 43% at CER to DKK 3,020 million.\n\nWithin Rare disease, rare endocrine disorder products increased by 19% in Danish kroner and by 24% at CER to DKK 5,959 million, while rare blood disorder products decreased by 2% in Danish kroner and increased by 2% at CER to DKK 11,955 million.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c2f9e2bf-4eb3-44bc-922b-8db97158fefa","uuid":"15ce79a4-024a-4314-989e-dbc008dd1933","timestamp":"2026-04-28T22:25:05.314Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk 2025 full year results revenue diabetes obesity rare disease segment DKK USD","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01HnCc9RbhojPxvTXFAwmG6F","content":[{"title":"Financial performance - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025","url":"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/strategic-aspirations/financial-performance.html"},{"title":"Investor presentation Full year 2025","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/pdfs/financial-results/2026/Q4-2025-investor-presentation-4Feb.pdf"},{"title":"securities and exchange commission","url":"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/353278/000035327826000006/caq42025.htm"},{"title":"Financial re