\n\n**Operating Cash Flow:**\n- 2024: $17.54B (10.92% increase from 2023)\n- 2023: $15.813B (41.57% increase from 2022)\n- 2022: $11.17B (27.65% increase from 2021)\n\n**Free Cash Flow:**\n- 2024: $10.702B (11.31% decline from 2023)\n- 2023: DKK 68.3 billion (compared to DKK -14.7 billion in 2024)\n\n**Capital Expenditure:**\n- 2024: $6.55 billion (up from $1.48 billion in 2018)\n\n**Important Context:**\nThe lower free cash flow in 2024 is mainly impacted by the USD 11.7 billion acquisition price related to the three Catalent manufacturing sites. Additionally, Novo is aggressively scaling up its production footprint, particularly in response to booming demand for GLP-1 drugs like Ozempic and Wegovy.\n\nThe search results don't provide specific detailed data for 2021 and 2025 for all metrics, though some partial information is available in the sources.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c2f9e2bf-4eb3-44bc-922b-8db97158fefa","uuid":"e2e0d5aa-cda1-4069-bed6-bca853be583d","timestamp":"2026-04-28T22:25:05.390Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk free cash flow capex operating cash flow 2021 2022 2023 2024 2025","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_019ZoQR25h3BqFeZx7cxKTyJ","content":[{"title":"Novo Nordisk Free Cash Flow 2012-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends","url":"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/free-cash-flow"},{"title":"Financials - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2024","url":"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2024/strategic-aspirations/financials.html"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Cash Flow Statement","url":"https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/nvo/financials/cash-flow-statement/"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Free Cash Flow Per Share 2011-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends","url":"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/free-cash-flow-per-share"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Cash Flow - Yahoo Finance - Yahoo Finance","url":"h