{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01B5SwJ3pANAGkyh2q3KA6wW","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk CEO Maziar Doustdar CFO Karsten Munk Knudsen compensation insider ownership shares 2025 2026\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Remuneration Report 2025 (PDF )\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/irmaterial/annual_report/2026/novo-nordisk-remuneration-report-2025.pdf\"},{\"title\":\"What did Big Pharma CEOs get paid in 2025?\",\"url\":\"https://www.mmm-online.com/news/big-pharma-ceo-compensation-2025/\"},{\"title\":\"Meet Novo Nordisk's Executive Management team\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/about/executive-management.html\"},{\"title\":\"Company announcement\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/nncorp/global/en/news-and-media/news-and-ir-materials/news-details.html?id=916408\"},{\"title\":\"NVO - Novo Nordisk AS ADR Executives | Morningstar\",\"url\":\"https://www.morningstar.com/stocks/xnys/nvo/executive\"},{\"title\":\"Executive Management - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/governance/executive-management.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk missed its diversity targets last year. Its CEO paid the price | Fortune\",\"url\":\"https://fortune.com/europe/2025/02/05/novo-nordisk-missed-dei-targets-last-year-ceo-paid-financial-price/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk CEO and Key Executive Team | Craft.co\",\"url\":\"https://craft.co/novo-nordisk/executives\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NOVO B) Leadership & Management Team Analysis - Simply Wall St\",\"url\":\"https://simplywall.st/stocks/dk/pharmaceuticals-biotech/cph-novo-b/novo-nordisk-shares/management\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Names New CEO; Makes Other Leadership Changes - DCAT Value Chain Insights\",\"url\":\"https://www.dcatvci.org/top-industry-news/novo-nordisk-names-new-ceo-makes-other-leadership-changes/\"}]\n\nI've completed the 