{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0151AucddFkctYVpKEzsbzqY","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk revenue by geography North America Europe international 2024 2025 percent breakdown\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk - Wikipedia\",\"url\":\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Novo_Nordisk\"},{\"title\":\"Financial performance - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/strategic-aspirations/financial-performance.html\"},{\"title\":\"Financials - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2024\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2024/strategic-aspirations/financials.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S: Business Segments and Geographical Breakdown of Revenue\",\"url\":\"https://www.marketscreener.com/quote/stock/NOVO-NORDISK-A-S-1412980/finances-segments/\"},{\"title\":\"Financial report for the period 1 January 2024 to 30 September 2024\",\"url\":\"https://ml-eu.globenewswire.com/Resource/Download/11f24e9a-5374-4abf-afc1-a31bc257a98a\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Revenue by Geography\",\"url\":\"https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/nvo/metrics/revenue-by-geography/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Operating Metrics & Breakdowns\",\"url\":\"https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/nvo/metrics/\"},{\"title\":\"Download financial workbook (xlsx)\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/pdfs/financial-results/2025/Q3-2025-financial-workbook.xlsx\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Revenue 2012-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends\",\"url\":\"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/revenue\"},{\"title\":\"Company announcement\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/news-and-media/news-and-ir-materials/news-details.html?id=167013\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, I found some information about Novo Nordisk's revenue and geographic operations, though the specific percentage breakdowns by geography for 2024 and 2025 are not fully detailed in these results.\n\nHere's what I found:\n\n**Overall Revenue:**\n- Net sales in 2024 were US$42.121 billion\n- Novo Nordisk annual revenue for 2025 was $46.792B, a 11.12% increase from 2024\n\n**Geographic Operations:**\nThe company organizes its geographic operations into several regions:\n- EUCAN covers Europe and Canada, Emerging Markets covers mainly Latin America, the Middle East and Africa\n- APAC covers Japan, Korea, Oceania, and Southeast Asia. Region China covers Mainland China, Hong Kong and Taiwan\n\n**Growth by Region (based on available data):**\n- Sales in North America Operations increased by 50% in Danish kroner (54% at CER)\n- Sales in International Operations increased by 11% in Danish kroner (16% at CER)\n\nUnfortunately, the search results do not contain the specific percentage breakdown of total revenue by geography (North America, Europe, and International as separate percentages) for 2024 and 2025. You may need to access Novo Nordisk's full Annual Reports or detailed investor presentations to find these exact figures.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c2f9e2bf-4eb3-44bc-922b-8db97158fefa","uuid":"eb5921a1-ef29-4bb8-9bef-da2d89bbcfa5","timestamp":"2026-04-28T22:26:51.352Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk revenue by geography North America Europe international 2024 2025 percent breakdown","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_016AJumxhh7eAESs17dLhCNj","content":[{"title":"Novo Nordisk - Wikipedia","url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Novo_Nordisk"},{"title":"Financial performance - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025","url":"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/strategic-aspirations/financial-performance.html"},{"title":"Financials - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2024","url":"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2024/strategic-aspirations/financials.html"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S: Business Segments and Geo