{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_018rf4Y7fWoXeCHxiMmCkpBk","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk NVO financial results 2025 revenue earnings annual\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Financial results and events overview - Novo Nordisk\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/investors/financial-results.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/investors/annual-report.html\"},{\"title\":\"Financial performance - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/strategic-aspirations/financial-performance.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Revenue 2012-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends\",\"url\":\"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/revenue\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025 (PDF)\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/irmaterial/annual_report/2026/novo-nordisk-annual-report-2025.pdf\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S Common Stock (NVO) Earnings Report Dates & Earnings Forecasts | Nasdaq\",\"url\":\"https://www.nasdaq.com/market-activity/stocks/nvo/earnings\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Earnings: Latest Report, Earnings Call & Financials\",\"url\":\"https://public.com/stocks/nvo/earnings\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Releases 2025 Financial Report and 2026 Sales and Operations Profit Outlook | PharmExec\",\"url\":\"https://www.pharmexec.com/view/novo-nordisk-2025-financial-report-2026-sales-operations-profit-outlook\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk's Strong Financial Performance Amidst... | FMP\",\"url\":\"https://site.financialmodelingprep.com/market-news/novo-nordisk-financial-performance-revenue-growth-2025\"},{\"title\":\"Q3-investor-presentation-2025.pdf\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/pdfs/financial-results/2025/Q3-investor-presentation-2025.pdf\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here are Novo Nordisk's (NVO) key 2025 financial results:\n\n## Revenue\nNovo Nordisk's annual revenue for 2025 was $46.792 billion, an 11.12% increase year-over-year. In Danish kroner, sales increased by 6% measured in Danish kroner and by 10% at constant exchange rates to DKK 309,064 million in 2025.\n\n## Earnings\nNet profit increased by 1% to DKK 102,434 million and diluted earnings per share increased by 2% to DKK 23.03. For Q4 2025 specifically, Novo Nordisk reported earnings per share (EPS) of $1, which exceeded analysts' expectations of $0.89 by 12.36%.\n\n## Cash Flow\nFree cash flow in 2025 was DKK 28.3 billion compared to DKK (14.7) billion in 2024.\n\n## Business Segment Performance\nSales of Obesity care products increased by 26% measured in Danish kroner and by 31% at constant exchange rates to DKK 82,347 million.\n\nNovo Nordisk posted strong 2025 sales growth driven by obesity treatments and U.S. market performance, but operating profits signal a more cautious outlook for 2026.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"eafad868-0c85-44e0-a96c-5a256a92aae5","uuid":"0d42dd64-586d-4e9b-8391-7259fc860c5e","timestamp":"2026-04-28T22:41:25.748Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk NVO financial results 2025 revenue earnings annual","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_018AgmraCdF3PhuzSU7kdAtV","content":[{"title":"Financial results and events overview - Novo Nordisk","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/investors/financial-results.html"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/investors/annual-report.html"},{"title":"Financial performance - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025","url":"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/strategic-aspirations/financial-performance.html"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Revenue 2012-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends","url":"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/revenue"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025 (PDF)","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/irmaterial/annual_report/2026/novo-nordisk-annual-report-2025.pdf"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S Common Stock (NVO) Earnings Report Dates & Earnings Forecasts | Nasdaq","url":"https://www.nasdaq.com/market-activity/stocks/nvo/earnings"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Earnings: Latest Report, Earnings Call & Financials","url":"https://public.com/stocks/nvo/earnings"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Releases 2025 Financial Report and 2026 Sales and Operations Profit Outlook | PharmExec","url":"https://www.pharmexec.com/view/novo-nordisk-2025-financial-report-2026-sales-operations-profit-outlook"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk's Strong Financial Performance Amidst... | FMP","url":"https://site.financialmodelingprep.com/market-news/novo-nordisk-financial-performance-revenue-growth-2025"},{"title":"Q3-investor-presentation-2025.pdf","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/pdfs/financial-results/2025/Q3-investor-presentation-2025.pdf"}]},"Based on the search results, here are Novo Nordisk's (NVO) key 2025 financial results:\n\n## Revenue\nNovo Nordisk's annual revenue for 2025 was $46.792 billion, an 11.12% increase year-over-year. In Danish kroner, sales increased by 6% measured in Danish kroner and by 10% at constant exchange rates to DKK 309,064 million in 2025.\n\n## Earnings\nNet profit increased by 1% to DKK 102,434 million and diluted earnings per share increased by 2% to DKK 23.03. For Q4 2025 specifically, Novo Nordisk reported earnings per share (EPS) of $1, which exceeded analysts' expectations of $0.89 by 12.36%.\n\n## Cash Flow\nFree cash flow in 2025 was DKK 28.3 billion compared to DKK (14.7) billion in 2024.\n\n## Business Segment Performance\nSales of Obesity care products increased by 26% measured in Danish kroner and by 31% at constant exchange rates to DKK 82,347 million.\n\nNovo Nordisk posted strong 2025 sales growth driven by obesity treatments and U.S. market performance, but operating profits signal a more cautious outlook for 2026."],"durationSeconds":5.956058208000003}}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_013QLCzGkL81k4EEUzzxbw1H","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"NVO Novo Nordisk stock price market cap 2026 analyst ratings price target\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Stock Forecast and Price Target 2026 $NVO\",\"url\":\"https://www.marketbeat.com/stocks/NYSE/NVO/forecast/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Stock Forecast: Analyst Ratings, Predictions & Price Target 2026\",\"url\":\"https://public.com/stocks/nvo/forecast-price-target\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Stock Forecast, Price Targets and Analysts Predictions - TipRanks.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.tipranks.com/stocks/nvo/forecast\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Stock Forecast & Analyst Price Targets\",\"url\":\"https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/nvo/forecast/\"},{\"title\":\"NVO Stock Price Prediction 2026, 2027 & 2030: Analyst Targets & Quantum Computing Outlook • Benzinga\",\"url\":\"https://www.benzinga.com/money/ozempic-novo-nordisk-stock-price-prediction\"},{\"title\":\"What is the current Price Target and Forecast for Novo Nordisk (NVO)\",\"url\":\"https://www.zacks.com/stock/research/NVO/price-target-stock-forecast\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Stock Price & Overview\",\"url\":\"https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/nvo/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Analyst Ratings, Estimates & Forecasts - Yahoo Finance\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NVO/analysis/\"},{\"title\":\"NVO Stock Quote Price and Forecast | CNN\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnn.com/markets/stocks/NVO\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Analyst Ratings and Price Targets | NYSE:NVO | Benzinga\",\"url\":\"https://www.benzinga.com/quote/NVO/analyst-ratings\"}]\n\nBased on the web search results, here's comprehensive information about Novo Nordisk (NVO) stock:\n\n## Current Stock Price\nAs of April 19, 2026, the latest closing price of Novo Nordisk stock was around $40.52, following a previous all-time high of $142 in June 2024.\n\n## Market Capitalization\nA market capitalization above $200 billion places NVO in the mega-capitalization category.\n\n## Analyst Price Targets\nThere is some variation in analyst price targets across different sources:\n\n- Currently, 16 analysts give it a consensus price target of $85.31 with the highest target at $160 by Cantor Fitzgerald and the lowest at $41 from Goldman Sachs.\n- The 4 analysts that cover Novo Nordisk stock have a consensus rating of \"Hold\" and an average price target of $51, which forecasts a 23.23% increase in the stock price over the next year.\n- NVO's current price target is $65.56.\n\n## Analyst Ratings\nAccording to 6 analysts, Novo Nordisk (NVO) has a Buy consensus rating as of Apr 25, 2026. However, other sources show mixed sentiment: Novo Nordisk has a consensus rating of Hold which is based on 1 buy ratings, 7 hold ratings and 0 sell ratings.\n\n## Recent Context\nNovo Nordisk's current stock price for April 2026 is around $41, which is a drop of around 246% from an all-time closing high of $142 in June of 2024. A significant factor is the imposition of U.S. tariffs on European pharmaceutical imports, including key Novo Nordisk drugs like Ozempic and Wegovy.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"eafad868-0c85-44e0-a96c-5a256a92aae5","uuid":"ec2c803e-aa68-4bfb-986e-5ea79a14f813","timestamp":"2026-04-28T22:41:29.252Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"NVO Novo Nordisk stock price market cap 2026 analyst ratings price target","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_011r4KNVMS7VTnM6iy7HDJvo","content":[{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Stock Forecast and Price Target 2026 $NVO","url":"https://www.marketbeat.com/stocks/NYSE/NVO/forecast/"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Stock Forecast: Analyst Ratings, Predictions & Price Target 2026","url":"https://public.com/stocks/nvo/forecast-price-target"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk (N