st Ratings\nAccording to 6 analysts, Novo Nordisk (NVO) has a Buy consensus rating as of Apr 25, 2026. However, other sources show mixed sentiment: Novo Nordisk has a consensus rating of Hold which is based on 1 buy ratings, 7 hold ratings and 0 sell ratings.\n\n## Recent Context\nNovo Nordisk's current stock price for April 2026 is around $41, which is a drop of around 246% from an all-time closing high of $142 in June of 2024. A significant factor is the imposition of U.S. tariffs on European pharmaceutical imports, including key Novo Nordisk drugs like Ozempic and Wegovy."],"durationSeconds":8.989544291999998}}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016CGuwuzrTV49T3g7Fbr7QE","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk business segments Ozempic Wegovy revenue breakdown 2024 2025\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk predicts milder growth in 2025 after obesity star Wegovy doubles sales in Q4 | Fierce Pharma\",\"url\":\"https://www.fiercepharma.com/pharma/novo-nordisk-predicts-milder-sales-growth-2025-after-obesity-star-wegovy-doubles-numbers-q4\"},{\"title\":\"Ozempic and Wegovy pumped $26 billion into Novo Nordisk last year. Can the pharma giant find its next breakthrough before the boom ends? | Fortune\",\"url\":\"https://fortune.com/2025/03/31/ozempic-wegovy-novo-nordisk-nvidia/\"},{\"title\":\"Slowing Ozempic, Wegovy sales lead to cut in top end of ...\",\"url\":\"https://firstwordpharma.com/story/6516083\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Semaglutide Revenue: How Ozempic and Wegovy Are Driving Record Profits - Pharmacy Business Hub\",\"url\":\"https://pharmabusinesshub.com/novo-nordisk-semaglutide-revenue/\"},{\"title\":\"The Heavy Price of GLP-1 Drugs: How Financialization Drives Pharmaceutical Patent Abuse and Health Inequities for GLP-1 Therapies\",\"url\":\"https://www.i-mak.org/glp-1/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk 2025: All in on weight loss - PharmaLive\",\"url\":\"https://www.pharmalive.com/novo-nordisk-2025-all-in-on-weight-loss/\"},{\"title\":\"Financial performance - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/strategic-aspirations/financial-performance.html\"},{\"title\":\"Financials - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2024\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2024/strategic-aspirations/financials.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk’s diabetes and weight loss drug sales growth decelerates\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/novo-nordisk-diabetes-weight-loss-121017710.html\"},{\"title\":\"Wegovy, Ozempic maker Novo Nordisk Q3 earnings; shares fall\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2025/11/05/wegovy-ozempic-maker-novo-nordisk-q3-earnings.html\"}]\n\nBased on the web search results, here's a comprehensive breakdown of Novo Nordisk's business segments with a focus on Ozempic and Wegovy revenue:\n\n## Revenue Breakdown for 2024\n\nFor all of 2024, global Wegovy sales totaled 58.2 billion kroner (around $8 billion), compared to 31.3 billion kroner the prior year. Comparatively, Ozempic brought home around 120 billion kroner (nearly $17 billion) over the same stretch.\n\nMore detailed figures show: Ozempic generated $17.45 billion in sales for the year, an improvement of 25.7 percent compared with 2023, and sales of Wegovy nearly doubled in 2024, from $4.55 billion to $8.44 billion.\n\n## Market Dominance\n\nA single compound accounted for almost 70 percent of Novo Nordisk's top-line revenue in 2024: semaglutide, in both its type 2 diabetes (Ozempic, Rybelsus) and weight loss (Wegovy) forms. Global sales of Novo Nordisk's top GLP-1 drugs, Ozempic and Wegovy, totaled $26 billion in 2024.\n\n## Business Segments and Other Products\n\nSales of Obesity care products, Wegovy and Saxenda, increased by 56% measured in Danish kroner and by 57% at CER to DKK 65,146 million. Novo's total insulin sales totaled 55.37 billion kroner ($7.7 billion) versus 48 billion kroner in 2023.\n\n## 2025 Performance and Outlook\n\nSales for the portfolio, which includes flagship diabetes treatment Ozempic and weight loss medication Wegovy, grew 16% to DKK 145.4bn ($22.57bn) in H1 2025. Novo narrowed its full-year guidance for the fourth time this year, saying it now expects sales growth within the range of 8% to 11% at constant exchange rates.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"eafad868-0c85-44e0-a96c-5a256a92aae5","uuid":"13ce2be4-40be-4260-b484-52a7c985b823","timestamp":"2026-04-28T22:41:32.042Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"No