{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01WTHAVFeuva4mDa5cSUchqD","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk NVO insider trading form 4 SEC 2025 2026 CEO shares owned\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S Insider Trading & Ownership Structure - Simply Wall St\",\"url\":\"https://simplywall.st/stocks/dk/pharmaceuticals-biotech/cph-novo-b/novo-nordisk-shares/ownership\"},{\"title\":\"NVO Insider Trading - Novo Nordisk A/S - Depositary Receipt (Common Stock)\",\"url\":\"https://fintel.io/sn/us/nvo\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Recent Insider Transactions - Yahoo Finance\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NVO/insider-transactions/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S - Insider Trading - Insider Transactions - Form 4\",\"url\":\"https://finviz.com/insidertrading.ashx?oc=353278\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S Common Stock (NVO) Insider Activity & Insider Shares Traded | Nasdaq\",\"url\":\"https://www.nasdaq.com/market-activity/stocks/nvo/insider-activity\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Insider Trading Activity 2026 $NVO\",\"url\":\"https://www.marketbeat.com/stocks/NYSE/NVO/insider-trades/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk AS (NVO) Stock Holders - Institutional & Insider Ownership | GuruFocus\",\"url\":\"https://www.gurufocus.com/stock/NVO/ownership\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk AS (NVO) Insider Trading Activity | Apple Insider Buys and Sells\",\"url\":\"https://www.gurufocus.com/stock/NVO/insider\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Insider Ownership & Holdings - Yahoo Finance\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NVO/insider-roster/\"},{\"title\":\"NVO - Novo Nordisk A/S - Depositary Receipt (Common Stock) Stock - Stock Price, Institutional Ownership, Shareholders (NYSE)\",\"url\":\"https://fintel.io/so/us/nvo\"}]\n\nBased on the web search results, I found information about Novo Nordisk (NVO) insider trading filing resources. Here's what the search revealed:\n\nInsiders must report all trades to the SEC via a Form 4. Several financial websites track this information for Novo Nordisk (NVO):\n\n1. **Fintel.io** - Shows a list of known insiders generated automatically from filings disclosed to the SEC.\n\n2. **Yahoo Finance** - Provides insider transaction data for NVO at their insider transactions and insider ownership pages\n\n3. **NASDAQ** - Offers insider activity and insider shares traded information\n\n4. **MarketBeat** - Displays the latest NVO insider trading activity\n\n5. **GuruFocus** - Tracks both insider trading activity and insider ownership history\n\nThe search results show these are aggregator websites that compile Form 4 filings from the SEC. To access specific Form 4 filings with detailed information about CEO share ownership and transactions in 2025-2026, you would want to visit the actual SEC Edgar database (sec.gov) or use one of these financial data platforms to see the most recent insider transactions and holdings for Novo Nordisk executives.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"eafad868-0c85-44e0-a96c-5a256a92aae5","uuid":"7f642aa6-28a0-4efd-8a31-892ee6288a3e","timestamp":"2026-04-28T22:42:29.916Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk NVO insider trading form 4 SEC 2025 2026 CEO shares owned","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01X1GgDBxwwwtijNdxFkBeMt","content":[{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S Insider Trading & Ownership Structure - Simply Wall St","url":"https://simplywall.st/stocks/dk/pharmaceuticals-biotech/cph-novo-b/novo-nordisk-shares/ownership"},{"title":"NVO Insider Trading - Novo Nordisk A/S - Depositary Receipt (Common Stock)","url":"https://fintel.io/sn/us/nvo"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Recent Insider Transactions - Yahoo Finance","url":"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NVO/insider-transactions/"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S - Insider Trading - Insider Transactions - Form 4","url":"htt