{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016rWhaSPaMAWLcJW2jySg7f","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk semaglutide loss of exclusivity 2026 guidance decline pipeline cagrilintide CagriSema\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Has Fallen 56% From Its High. Is NVO Finally Cheap Enough to Buy in 2026? | TIKR.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.tikr.com/blog/novo-nordisk-has-fallen-56-from-its-high-is-nvo-finally-cheap-enough-to-buy-in-2026\"},{\"title\":\"TD Cowen downgrades Novo Nordisk on concerns over semaglutide patent loss, pipeline outlook\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/10/td-cowen-downgrades-novo-nordisk-on-concerns-over-semaglutide-patent-loss.html\"},{\"title\":\"News Details\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/nncorp/global/en/news-and-media/news-and-ir-materials/news-details.html?id=915995\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk: Downgrading To 'Sell' As GLP-1 Pipeline Faces Many Risks (NYSE:NVO) | Seeking Alpha\",\"url\":\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4888549-novo-nordisk-downgrading-to-sell-as-glp-1-pipeline-faces-many-risks\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Submits NDA to FDA for CagriSema | PharmExec\",\"url\":\"https://www.pharmexec.com/view/novo-nordisk-submits-nda-fda-cagrisema\"},{\"title\":\"Healthy Returns: What’s next for Novo Nordisk’s next-generation obesity drug CagriSema after trial miss\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/02/24/healthy-returns-whats-next-for-novo-nordisks-obesity-drug-cagrisema.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Downgrade: Semaglutide Patent Risks in 2026\",\"url\":\"https://capwolf.com/novo-nordisk-downgrade-semaglutide-patent-risks-in-2026/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk: CagriSema, Price Cuts, and the End of Pipeline Superiority?\",\"url\":\"https://insights.woozleresearch.com/novo-nordisk-cagrisema-price-cuts-and-the-end-of-pipeline-superiority/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk files for FDA approval of CagriSema, the first once-weekly combination of GLP‑1 and amylin analogues for weight management\",\"url\":\"https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/novo-nordisk-files-for-fda-approval-of-cagrisema-the-first-once-weekly-combination-of-glp1-and-amylin-analogues-for-weight-management-302645862.html\"},{\"title\":\"CagriSema: 22.7% Weight Loss in Phase 3 Trials | FDA Timeline & Results\",\"url\":\"https://www.findhonestcare.com/metabolic-innovations/cagrisema/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's a comprehensive overview of the key topics you asked about:\n\n## CagriSema Pipeline Setback\n\nCagriSema, Novo Nordisk's next-generation weight-loss drug combining semaglutide and cagrilintide, failed to demonstrate non-inferiority against Eli Lilly's tirzepatide in the Phase 3 REDEFINE 4 trial on February 23, 2026. CagriSema achieved 23% weight loss after 84 weeks but did not meet the primary endpoint of non-inferiority compared to tirzepatide.\n\nThe impact was significant: The stock fell over 16% after the CagriSema failure. Goldman Sachs cut peak sales expectations for CagriSema and cagrilintide monotherapy from approximately $11.8 billion to $5.2 billion, with obesity peak sales alone falling from $7.5 billion to $3 billion.\n\n## 2026 Guidance and Revenue Decline\n\nNovo Nordisk's 2026 outlook shows adjusted sales and operating profit are both expected to decline between 5% and 13% at constant exchange rates. CEO Maziar Doustdar told investors that \"Price reduction, in some ways, is our investment for the future and for capturing more patients,\" and guiding for the first revenue decline in the GLP-1 era was a genuine shock.\n\nNovo's 2026 guidance reflects significantly lower U.S. pricing from the Most-Favored-Nations pricing framework, reduced Medicaid coverage of anti-obesity medicines, and Novo's own decision to cut Wegovy and Ozempic list prices by up to 50% starting January 2027.\n\n## Semaglutide Loss of Exclusivity\n\nNovo Nordisk's semaglutide patent is secured through 2032, however, it expires in several countries later this month (March 2026). Several important countries see patents expiring much sooner—starting as early as this year in places like India, China, Canada, Brazil, and others.\n\nAnalysts note that \"the business faces enormous challenges — first from branded competition, then from semaglutide LOE — and it is no longer clear the pipeline can answer the call,\" with \"CagriSema, amycretin, ziltivekimab all have meaningful potential, but do not combine to create a compelling post-sema trajectory.\"\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"eafad868-0c85-44e0-a96c-5a256a92aae5","uuid":"a41dd8a3-add6-45f8-b11d-593ef9998276","timestamp":"2026-04-28T22:42:56.298Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk semaglutide loss of exclusivity 2026 guidance decline pipeline cagrilintide CagriSema","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01Ee33sYxSb8WNkepeYEqSmu","content":[{"title":"Novo Nordisk Has Fallen 56% From Its High. Is NVO Finally Cheap Enough to Buy in 2026? | TIKR.com","url":"https://www.tikr.com/blog/novo-nordisk-has-fallen-56-from-its-high-is-nvo-finally-cheap-enough-to-buy-in-2026"},{"title":"TD Cowen downgrades Novo Nordisk on concerns over semaglutide patent loss, pipeline outlook","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/10/td-cowen-downgrades-novo-nordisk-on-concerns-over-semaglutide-patent-loss.html"},{"title":"News Details","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/nncorp/global/en/news-and-media/news-and-ir-materials/news-details.html?id=915995"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk: Downgrading To 'Sell' As GLP-1 Pipeline Faces Many Risks (NYSE:NVO) | Seeking Alpha","url":"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4888549-novo-nordisk-downgrading-to-sell-as-glp-1-pipeline-faces-many-risks"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Submits NDA to FDA for CagriSema | PharmExec","url":"https://www.pharmexec.com/view/novo-nordisk-submits-nda-fda-cagrisema"},{"title":"Healthy Returns: 