{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_015eh61YKma74gBrKEznpNzk","type":"tool_result","content":"# Novo Nordisk 2025 Financial Breakdown\n\n## Geographic Revenue Breakdown\n\nThe document provides **regional sales data** rather than traditional North America/Europe/China/Rest of World categories:\n\n- **US Operations**: Increased 3% in DKK, 8% at CER\n- **International Operations**: Increased 10% in DKK, 14% at CER\n  - EUCAN: +15% DKK, +16% CER\n  - Emerging Markets: +3% DKK, +8% CER\n  - APAC: +19% DKK, +25% CER\n  - Region China: +1% DKK, +5% CER\n\n**Total 2025 Sales**: DKK 309,064 million\n\n## Product Revenue Breakdown\n\nOnly specific products are detailed:\n\n- **Ozempic®**: DKK 127,089 million (+6% DKK, +10% CER)\n- **Rybelsus®**: DKK 22,093 million (-5% DKK, -2% CER)\n- **Victoza®**: DKK 3,020 million (-45% DKK, -43% CER)\n\nAggregate therapeutic area revenues are provided, but individual revenues for Wegovy®, Tresiba, and NovoRapid/Novolog are **not separately disclosed** in this document.\n\n## 2026 Guidance\n\n- **Adjusted Sales Growth**: -5% to -13% at CER\n- **Adjusted Operating Profit Growth**: -5% to -13% at CER\n- **Free Cash Flow**: DKK 35-45 billion\n- **Capital Expenditure**: ~DKK 55 billion\n- **Effective Tax Rate**: 21-23%"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"eafad868-0c85-44e0-a96c-5a256a92aae5","uuid":"896e3825-7aea-4423-92e0-d90aad5568ae","timestamp":"2026-04-28T22:43:08.951Z","tool_use_result":{"bytes":386579,"code":200,"codeText":"OK","result":"# Novo Nordisk 2025 Financial Breakdown\n\n## Geographic Revenue Breakdown\n\nThe document provides **regional sales data** rather than traditional North America/Europe/China/Rest of World categories:\n\n- **US Operations**: Increased 3% in DKK, 8% at CER\n- **International Operations**: Increased 10% in DKK, 14% at CER\n  - EUCAN: +15% DKK, +16% CER\n  - Emerging Markets: +3% DKK, +8% CER\n  - APAC: +19% DKK, +25% CER\n  - Region China: +1% DKK, +5% CER\n\n**Total 2025 Sales**: DKK 309,064 million\n\n## Product Revenue Breakdown\n\nOnly specific products are detailed:\n\n- **Ozempic®**: DKK 127,089 million (+6% DKK, +10% CER)\n- **Rybelsus®**: DKK 22,093 million (-5% DKK, -2% CER)\n- **Victoza®**: DKK 3,020 million (-45% DKK, -43% CER)\n\nAggregate therapeutic area revenues are provided, but individual revenues for Wegovy®, Tresiba, and NovoRapid/Novolog are **not separately disclosed** in this document.\n\n## 2026 Guidance\n\n- **Adjusted Sales Growth**: -5% to -13% at CER\n- **Adjusted Operating Profit Growth**: -5% to -13% at CER\n- **Free Cash Flow**: DKK 35-45 billion\n- **Capital Expenditure**: ~DKK 55 billion\n- **Effective Tax Rate**: 21-23%","durationMs":4901,"url":"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/strategic-aspirations/financial-performance.html"}}
