{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01W5UwQaeP8FVWnJY91iS9NG","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk NVO Wegovy 2025 annual sales DKK billion obesity care full year\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Exact name of Registrant as specified in its charter\",\"url\":\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/353278/000035327825000005/caq32025.htm\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk: Wegovy sales by quarter 2025\",\"url\":\"https://www.statista.com/statistics/1416998/sales-wegovy-novo-nordisk-by-quarter/\"},{\"title\":\"Financial performance - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/strategic-aspirations/financial-performance.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk shares rise on fourth-quarter profit beat, Wegovy sales jump\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2025/02/05/novo-nordisk-nvo-earnings-q4-full-year-fy24.html\"},{\"title\":\"Financial report for the period 1 January 2025 to 30 September 2025\",\"url\":\"https://ml-eu.globenewswire.com/Resource/Download/ae93d17e-6c68-433e-ac46-9ea814575af0\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Q3 2025 Earnings Transcript | The Motley Fool\",\"url\":\"https://www.fool.com/earnings/call-transcripts/2025/12/11/novo-nordisk-nvo-q3-2025-earnings-transcript/\"},{\"title\":\"How Will Ozempic and Wegovy Sales Aid NVO's Upcoming Q4 Results?\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/ozempic-wegovy-sales-aid-nvos-141500549.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk's sales increased by 6% in Danish kroner and by 10% at constant exchange rates to DKK 309.1 billion in 2025\",\"url\":\"https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2026/2/3/3231383/0/en/Novo-Nordisk-s-sales-increased-by-6-in-Danish-kroner-and-by-10-at-constant-exchange-rates-to-DKK-309-1-billion-in-2025.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk predicts milder growth in 2025 after obesity star Wegovy doubles sales in Q4 | Fierce Pharma\",\"url\":\"https://www.fiercepharma.com/pharma/novo-nordisk-predicts-milder-sales-growth-2025-after-obesity-star-wegovy-doubles-numbers-q4\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Top Selling Products 2025\",\"url\":\"https://www.accio.com/business/novo-nordisk-top-selling-products\"}]\n\nBased on the web search results, here's the information about Novo Nordisk's Wegovy sales and obesity care performance for 2025:\n\n## Full Year 2025 Results\n\nObesity care growth reached 26% in Danish kroner (31% at constant exchange rates) for the full year 2025, with total sales within Obesity and Diabetes care reaching DKK 289.5 billion (10% at CER).\n\n## Nine-Month 2025 Performance\n\nDuring the first nine months of 2025, Obesity care sales grew 37% in Danish kroner to DKK 59.9 billion (41% at CER), driven by Wegovy.\n\n## Q3 2025 Performance\n\nSales of Wegovy reached approximately DKK 20 billion growing at 168% in Q3 2025, driven by sales growth across all regions.\n\n## Wegovy's Strategic Importance\n\nOn 22 December, the US FDA approved the first oral GLP-1 in obesity, once-daily oral semaglutide 25 mg, under the brand name of Wegovy pill, which represents a significant expansion opportunity for the obesity care business going forward.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"eafad868-0c85-44e0-a96c-5a256a92aae5","uuid":"ff6a50fb-feeb-48ff-89c9-a8f3668c3667","timestamp":"2026-04-28T22:43:29.147Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk NVO Wegovy 2025 annual sales DKK billion obesity care full year","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_011LrMEeL2huxDrR3wEePprT","content":[{"title":"Exact name of Registrant as specified in its charter","url":"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/353278/000035327825000005/caq32025.htm"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk: Wegovy sales by quarter 2025","url":"https://www.statista.com/statistics/1416998/sales-wegovy-novo-nordisk-by-quarter/"},{"title":"Financial performance - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025","url":"https:/