 what I found regarding Novo Nordisk (NVO) analyst ratings and price targets for 2026 from the major banks you mentioned:\n\n## Overall Consensus\n\nNovo Nordisk AS has a consensus price target of $85.31 based on the ratings of 16 analysts.\n\n## Individual Bank Ratings and Price Targets\n\n**Goldman Sachs:**\nGoldman Sachs issued a price target low of $41 on March 2, 2026, changing their price target from $63 to $41. Goldman Sachs reaffirmed a Neutral rating on NVO and cut its 12-month price target to $41 from $63, citing mounting GLP-1 pricing headwinds and a deteriorating near-term revenue trajectory.\n\n**Morgan Stanley:**\nMorgan Stanley upgraded Novo Nordisk to Equal-weight from Underweight, assigning a $40 price target. The firm said the recent sell-off has better priced in mid-term risks, including concentration around semaglutide and the planned halving of Wegovy's US list price in 2027.\n\n**JPMorgan:**\nJ.P. Morgan downgraded Novo Nordisk to Neutral from Overweight, cutting its June 2027 NVO stock forecast to DKK 250 from DKK 350.\n\n## Overall Rating Distribution\n\nNovo Nordisk (NVO) has been analyzed by 6 analysts, with a consensus rating of Buy. 33% of analysts recommend a Strong Buy, 17% recommend Buy, 33% suggest Holding, 17% advise Selling, and 0% predict a Strong Sell.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"eafad868-0c85-44e0-a96c-5a256a92aae5","uuid":"b1413db9-8355-4d94-8fa8-2076d2d2403d","timestamp":"2026-04-28T22:44:03.547Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk NVO analyst ratings 2026 Morgan Stanley Goldman Sachs JPMorgan price target","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01Mnkhv2gZFofNkWrBMUkjw3","content":[{"title":"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Stock Forecast: Analyst Ratings, Predictions & Price Target 2026","url":"https://public.com/stocks/nvo/forecast-price-target"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Analyst Ratings and Price Targets | NYSE:NVO | B