{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01FenVEb9eeMK8gAn36VxGnD","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk 2025 annual report segment revenue diabetes obesity biopharmaceuticals breakdown\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Financial performance - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/strategic-aspirations/financial-performance.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025 - Home\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025 (PDF)\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/irmaterial/annual_report/2026/novo-nordisk-annual-report-2025.pdf\"},{\"title\":\"Financial report for the period 1 January 2025 to 30 September 2025\",\"url\":\"https://ml-eu.globenewswire.com/Resource/Download/ae93d17e-6c68-433e-ac46-9ea814575af0\"},{\"title\":\"securities and exchange commission\",\"url\":\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/353278/000035327826000006/caq42025.htm\"},{\"title\":\"Exact name of Registrant as specified in its charter\",\"url\":\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/353278/000162828025038087/caq22025.htm\"},{\"title\":\"Q3-investor-presentation-2025.pdf\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/pdfs/financial-results/2025/Q3-investor-presentation-2025.pdf\"},{\"title\":\"Financials - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2024\",\"url\":\"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2024/strategic-aspirations/financials.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk – a focused healthcare company Investor presentation\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/pdfs/financial-results/2025/Q1-2025-investor-presentation.pdf\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk details 2025 results and GLP‑1 growth | NVO SEC Filing - Form 20-F\",\"url\":\"https://www.stocktitan.net/sec-filings/NVO/20-f-novo-nordisk-a-s-files-annual-report-foreign-issuer-3e3a4c2d4e89.html\"}]\n\nBased on Novo Nordisk's 2025 annual report, here's the segment revenue breakdown for diabetes and obesity care:\n\n## Full Year 2025 Results\n\nSales within Obesity and Diabetes care increased by 7% in Danish kroner to DKK 289.5 billion (10% at CER), mainly driven by Obesity care growth of 26% in Danish kroner (31% at CER) and GLP-1 diabetes sales growing 2% in Danish kroner (6% at CER).\n\n### Obesity Care Segment\nSales of Obesity care products increased by 26% measured in Danish kroner and by 31% at CER to DKK 82,347 million. Wegovy® sales reached DKK 79,106 million in 2025.\n\n### Diabetes Care Segment\nSales in Diabetes care remained unchanged in Danish kroner and increased by 4% at CER. Ozempic® reached DKK 127,089 million in 2025.\n\n## Market Position\n\nNovo Nordisk is the global market leader with a branded volume market share of 59.6% in the obesity care segment, reflecting the strong performance of their GLP-1 portfolio across both therapeutic areas.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2207cdf7-0767-4a59-9a1b-a30564847c67","uuid":"230b426e-ed5e-4760-9084-b620a92de053","timestamp":"2026-04-28T23:21:22.961Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk 2025 annual report segment revenue diabetes obesity biopharmaceuticals breakdown","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01J7GirtvyZTe7D8WBJr3Eo5","content":[{"title":"Financial performance - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025","url":"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/strategic-aspirations/financial-performance.html"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025 - Home","url":"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2025/"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2025 (PDF)","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/irmaterial/annual_report/2026/novo-nordisk-annual-report-2025.pdf"},{"title":"Financial report for the period 1 January 2025 to 30 September 2025","url":"https://ml-eu.globenewswire.com/Resource/Download/ae93d17e-6c68-433e-ac46-9ea814575af0"},{"title":"securities and exchange commission","url":"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/353278/000035327826000006/caq42025.htm"},{"title":"Exact name of Registrant as specified in its charter","url":"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/353278/000162828025038087/caq22025.htm"},{"title":"Q3-investor-presentation-2025.pdf","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/pdfs/financial-results/2025/Q3-investor-presentation-2025.pdf"},{"title":"Financials - Novo Nordisk Annual Report 2024","url":"https://annualreport.novonordisk.com/2024/strategic-aspirations/financials.html"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk – a focused healthcare company Investor presentation","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/dam/nncorp/global/en/investors/pdfs/financial-results/2025/Q1-2025-investor-presentation.pdf"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk details 2025 results and GLP‑1 growth | NVO SEC Filing - Form 20-F","url":"https://www.stocktitan.net/sec-filings/NVO/20-f-novo-nordisk-a-s-files-annual-report-foreign-issuer-3e3a4c2d4e89.html"}]},"Based on Novo Nordisk's 2025 annual report, here's the segment revenue breakdown for diabetes and obesity care:\n\n## Full Year 2025 Results\n\nSales within Obesity and Diabetes care increased by 7% in Danish kroner to DKK 289.5 billion (10% at CER), mainly driven by Obesity care growth of 26% in Danish kroner (31% at CER) and GLP-1 diabetes sales growing 2% in Danish kroner (6% at CER).\n\n### Obesity Care Segment\nSales of Obesity care products increased by 26% measured in Danish kroner and by 31% at CER to DKK 82,347 million. Wegovy® sales reached DKK 79,106 million in 2025.\n\n### Diabetes Care Segment\nSales in Diabetes care remained unchanged in Danish kroner and increased by 4% at CER. Ozempic® reached DKK 127,089 million in 2025.\n\n## Market Position\n\nNovo Nordisk is the global market leader with a branded volume market share of 59.6% in the obesity care segment, reflecting the strong performance of their GLP-1 portfolio across both therapeutic areas."],"durationSeconds":6.005737458999996}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01UzPVaGir9PiAzG8ebcKEK9","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I'm getting detailed data. Let me now search for more data on management, insider transactions, competitive analysis, valuation multiples, and risks. I also need the US dollar conversion for the financial data.\n\nKey data so far:\n- NVO price: $41.28 (April 27, 2026)\n- Market cap: $182.78B\n- 52-week range: $35.12 - $81.44\n- Revenue 2025: $46.8B USD (DKK 309,064M)\n- Revenue 2024: $42.1B USD (DKK 290,403M)\n\n\n- Gross margin 2025: 81%\n- Net income 2025: ~$15.5B USD (DKK 102,434M)\n- EPS diluted 2025: DKK 23.03\n- Obesity segment: DKK 82,347M (Wegovy DKK 79,106M)\n- Diabetes segment: DKK ~207,153M (including Ozempic DKK 127,089M)\n- Strong GLP-1 market leader: 59.6% volume market share in obesity\n- Cash 2025: 26,464M DKK\n\nLooking at the balance sheet, total assets came to 542.9B DKK with long-term debt of 119B DKK and equity of 194B DKK. On the cash flow side, operating cash flow hit 119.1B DKK while capital expenditures jumped significantly to 60.1B DKK, leaving free cash flow of about 59B DKK. I'm also calculating the USD conversion rate using the revenue figures—looks like the DKK strengthened slightly from 2024 to 2025, around 4.4% appreciation. Now I'm converting the DKK figures to USD using the appropriate exchange rates for each year. For 2025, multiplying the DKK amounts by 0.1514 gives me the revenue of $46.8B along with corresponding gross profit, operating income, EBITDA, and net income figures. For 2024, I'm applying the 0.145 rate to get the $42.1B revenue figure.\n\nI need to find historical DKK/USD conversion rates to calculate the earlier years' figures in USD, or I could look up those revenue numbers directly from financial databases like Macrotrends. I'm also planning to gather additional data including management information and analyst ratings from TipRanks to complete the analysis.\n\nNow I'm compiling the remaining data points: competitive positioning and risk factors, valuation multiples for comparison, forward guidance for 2026, insider trading activity, and how revenue breaks down across different geographic regions.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2750,"cache_read_input_tokens":39624,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2750},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2207cdf7-0767-4a59-9a1b-a30564847c67","uuid":"189959ea-aa7a-4d1c-ad33-5b6a8e220e27"}
