{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01NZqp468iKYHg69mpwPAtcr","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk CEO Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen CFO management team 2025 proxy compensation ownership\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Company announcement\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/nncorp/global/en/news-and-media/news-and-ir-materials/news-details.html?id=916408\"},{\"title\":\"Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen - Wikipedia\",\"url\":\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lars_Fruergaard_J%C3%B8rgensen\"},{\"title\":\"Meet Novo Nordisk's Executive Management team\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/about/executive-management.html\"},{\"title\":\"Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/about/executive-management/lars-fruergaard-jorgensen.html\"},{\"title\":\"Will New CEO's Leadership Propel Novo Nordisk's Next Growth Wave?\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/ceos-leadership-propel-novo-nordisks-130600201.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Names New CEO; Makes Other Leadership Changes - DCAT Value Chain Insights\",\"url\":\"https://www.dcatvci.org/top-industry-news/novo-nordisk-names-new-ceo-makes-other-leadership-changes/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NOVO B) Leadership & Management Team Analysis - Simply Wall St\",\"url\":\"https://simplywall.st/stocks/dk/pharmaceuticals-biotech/cph-novo-b/novo-nordisk-shares/management\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Leadership & Management Team Analysis - Simply Wall St\",\"url\":\"https://simplywall.st/stocks/us/pharmaceuticals-biotech/nyse-nvo/novo-nordisk/management\"},{\"title\":\"Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen | ISPE | International Society for Pharmaceutical Engineering\",\"url\":\"https://ispe.org/people/lars-fruergaard-jorgensen\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk missed its diversity targets last year. Its CEO paid the price | Fortune\",\"url\":\"https://fortune.com/europe/2025/02/05/novo-nordisk-missed-dei-targets-last-year-ceo-paid-financial-price/\"}]\n\nBased on the web search results, here's what I found regarding Novo Nordisk's leadership and management:\n\n## CEO and Leadership Changes\n\nMaziar Mike Doustdar has been appointed as president and chief executive officer, effective 7 August 2025, succeeding Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen, who stepped down as president and chief executive officer on the same date. Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen was the chief executive of Novo Nordisk between January 2017 and August 2025.\n\n## Executive Management Structure\n\nNovo Nordisk merged its Research & Early Development with its Development area into a new, consolidated R&D unit, under the leadership of Martin Holst Lange, MD, PhD, who was appointed chief scientific officer (CSO), effective 7 August. Emil Kongshøj Larsen, currently senior vice president of the Europe and Canada region (EUCAN), joined Executive Management and succeeded Mike Doustdar, assuming the responsibility of executive vice president, International Operations.\n\n## CFO and Compensation\n\nNovo Nordisk's CFO is Karsten Munk Knudsen. \n\nRegarding CEO compensation: Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen received a total remuneration package of DKK 57.1 million ($7.97 million) in 2024, of which 42% is not yet finally determined, and 45% is deferred.\n\n## Ownership\n\nNovo Nordisk's CEO Maziar Doustdar, appointed in Aug 2025, directly owns 0.002% of the company's shares, worth $4.67M.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2207cdf7-0767-4a59-9a1b-a30564847c67","uuid":"32c0203f-5769-4d7a-bff1-534951a3ea7a","timestamp":"2026-04-28T23:21:50.629Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk CEO Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen CFO management team 2025 proxy compensation ownership","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01XLmsx9TwJPSuTDuiyZfwsn","content":[{"title":"Company announcement","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/content/nncorp/global/en/news-and-media/news-and-ir-materials/news-details.html?id=916408"},{"title":"Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen - Wikipedia","url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lars_Fruergaard_J%C3%B8rgensen"},{"title":"Meet Novo Nordisk's Executive Management team","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/about/executive-management.html"},{"title":"Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/about/executive-management/lars-fruergaard-jorgensen.html"},{"title":"Will New CEO's Leadership Propel Novo Nordisk's Next Growth Wave?","url":"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/ceos-leadership-propel-novo-nordisks-130600201.html"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Names New CEO; Makes Other Leadership Changes - DCAT Value Chain Insights","url":"https://www.dcatvci.org/top-industry-news/novo-nordisk-names-new-ceo-makes-other-leadership-changes/"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S (NOVO B) Leadership & Management Team Analysis - Simply Wall St","url":"https://simplywall.st/stocks/dk/pharmaceuticals-biotech/cph-novo-b/novo-nordisk-shares/management"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Leadership & Management Team Analysis - Simply Wall St","url":"https://simplywall.st/stocks/us/pharmaceuticals-biotech/nyse-nvo/novo-nordisk/management"},{"title":"Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen | ISPE | International Society for Pharmaceutical Engineering","url":"https://ispe.org/people/lars-fruergaard-jorgensen"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk missed its diversity targets last year. Its CEO paid the price | Fortune","url":"https://fortune.com/europe/2025/02/05/novo-nordisk-missed-dei-targets-last-year-ceo-paid-financial-price/"}]},"Based on the web search results, here's what I found regarding Novo Nordisk's leadership and management:\n\n## CEO and Leadership Changes\n\nMaziar Mike Doustdar has been appointed as president and chief executive officer, effective 7 August 2025, succeeding Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen, who stepped down as president and chief executive officer on the same date. Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen was the chief executive of Novo Nordisk between January 2017 and August 2025.\n\n## Executive Management Structure\n\nNovo Nordisk merged its Research & Early Development with its Development area into a new, consolidated R&D unit, under the leadership of Martin Holst Lange, MD, PhD, who was appointed chief scientific officer (CSO), effective 7 August. Emil Kongshøj Larsen, currently senior vice president of the Europe and Canada region (EUCAN), joined Executive Management and succeeded Mike Doustdar, assuming the responsibility of executive vice president, International Operations.\n\n## CFO and Compensation\n\nNovo Nordisk's CFO is Karsten Munk Knudsen. \n\nRegarding CEO compensation: Lars Fruergaard Jørgensen received a total remuneration package of DKK 57.1 million ($7.97 million) in 2024, of which 42% is not yet finally determined, and 45% is deferred.\n\n## Ownership\n\nNovo Nordisk's CEO Maziar Doustdar, appointed in Aug 2025, directly owns 0.002% of the company's shares, worth $4.67M."],"durationSeconds":7.076118958000007}}
