{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01CKP6jveyjL9w8m8DHdzfwd","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk return on equity ROE ROA ROIC 2021 2022 2023 2024 2025\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S ROIC | NOV.DE\",\"url\":\"https://mlq.ai/stocks/NOV.DE/roic/\"},{\"title\":\"NVO (Novo Nordisk AS) ROIC %: 21.14% (As of Dec. 2025)\",\"url\":\"https://www.gurufocus.com/term/roic/NVO\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk Return on Investment 2012-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends\",\"url\":\"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/roi\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Average ROE\",\"url\":\"https://www.wisesheets.io/roe/NVO\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Financial Ratios\",\"url\":\"https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/nvo/financials/ratios/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) ROIC - Current & Historical Data (Mar 2026)\",\"url\":\"https://www.financecharts.com/stocks/NVO/value/roic\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk ROE - Return on Equity 2012-2025 | NVO\",\"url\":\"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/roe\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Statistics & Valuation\",\"url\":\"https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/nvo/statistics/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S - ROE\",\"url\":\"https://www.wisesheets.io/roe/NOVO-B.CO\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NYSE:NVO) Return on Common Equity - Investing.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.investing.com/pro/NYSE:NVO/explorer/roe\"}]\n\nI found search results with information about Novo Nordisk's return on equity (ROE), return on assets (ROA), and return on invested capital (ROIC) metrics. Here's what the data shows:\n\n## Current Metrics (Most Recent)\n\nNovo Nordisk's Return on Equity (ROE) stands at 61.10% and Return on Assets (ROA) at 18.87%. The company's trailing twelve-month (TTM) Return on Invested Capital (ROIC) is 29.53%.\n\nAlternatively, ROIC for December 2025 is 21.14%, and ROE is 60.70% with ROIC at 41.13%, showing some variation depending on the source and calculation method.\n\n## Historical ROE Trends (2021-2025)\n\nNovo Nordisk's return on common equity increased in 2021 (71.2%), 2022 (72.0%), and 2023 (88.1%), and decreased in 2024 (80.8%) and 2025 (60.7%). The company's return on common equity peaked in December 2023 at 88.1%.\n\nThe data shows that Novo Nordisk's profitability metrics have been relatively strong, though ROE has declined from its 2023 peak. The variation in reported numbers reflects different calculation methods and time periods used by various financial data providers.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2207cdf7-0767-4a59-9a1b-a30564847c67","uuid":"f983aa72-2265-4c9e-b393-9137abd327aa","timestamp":"2026-04-28T23:22:24.882Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk return on equity ROE ROA ROIC 2021 2022 2023 2024 2025","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01BWaSkkhrNqdEHHumTKf5xu","content":[{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S ROIC | NOV.DE","url":"https://mlq.ai/stocks/NOV.DE/roic/"},{"title":"NVO (Novo Nordisk AS) ROIC %: 21.14% (As of Dec. 2025)","url":"https://www.gurufocus.com/term/roic/NVO"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk Return on Investment 2012-2025 | NVO | MacroTrends","url":"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/roi"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S (NVO) Average ROE","url":"https://www.wisesheets.io/roe/NVO"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Financial Ratios","url":"https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/nvo/financials/ratios/"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk (NVO) ROIC - Current & Historical Data (Mar 2026)","url":"https://www.financecharts.com/stocks/NVO/value/roic"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk ROE - Return on Equity 2012-2025 | NVO","url":"https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/NVO/novo-nordisk/roe"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk (NVO) Statistics & Valuation","url":"https://stockanalysis.com/stocks/nvo/statistics/"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S - ROE","url":"https://www.wi