{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0137XXejjPChrviBMuZ2r7kw","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Novo Nordisk Q4 2025 earnings call transcript guidance 2026 key highlights\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Financial results and events overview - Novo Nordisk\",\"url\":\"https://www.novonordisk.com/investors/financial-results.html\"},{\"title\":\"Earnings call transcript: Novo Nordisk Q4 2025 beats EPS and revenue forecasts By Investing.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.investing.com/news/transcripts/earnings-call-transcript-novo-nordisk-q4-2025-beats-eps-and-revenue-forecasts-93CH-4484819\"},{\"title\":\"Q4 2025 Novo Nordisk A/S Earnings Call Transcript\",\"url\":\"https://www.gurufocus.com/stock/XTER:NOV/transcripts/8582161\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NOVO:CA) Q4 2025 Earnings Call Transcript | Seeking Alpha\",\"url\":\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4866503-novo-nordisk-a-s-novo-ca-q4-2025-earnings-call-transcript\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S (NYSE:NVO) Q4 2025 Earnings Call Transcript - Insider Monkey\",\"url\":\"https://www.insidermonkey.com/blog/novo-nordisk-a-s-nysenvo-q4-2025-earnings-call-transcript-1690199/\"},{\"title\":\"NOVO NORDISK A/S (NVON.MX) Q4 FY2025 earnings call transcript\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NVON.MX/earnings/NVON.MX-Q4-2025-earnings_call-373247.html\"},{\"title\":\"NOVO-NORDISK AS I (NOVA.F) Q4 FY2025 earnings call transcript\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NOVA.F/earnings/NOVA.F-Q4-2025-earnings_call-373247.html\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S Q4 2025 Earnings Call Transcript\",\"url\":\"https://www.marketbeat.com/earnings/reports/2026-2-3-novo-nordisk-as-stock/\"},{\"title\":\"Novo Nordisk A/S – Transcripts – BamSEC\",\"url\":\"https://www.bamsec.com/companies/353278/novo-nordisk-a-s/transcripts\"},{\"title\":\"Novo-Nordisk AS (NOV.SG) Q4 FY2025 earnings call transcript\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NOV.SG/earnings/NOV.SG-Q4-2025-earnings_call-373247.html\"}]\n\nBased on the Q4 2025 earnings call transcript, here are the key highlights and 2026 guidance for Novo Nordisk:\n\n## 2026 Guidance\n\nNovo Nordisk anticipates adjusted sales growth between -5% and -13% at constant exchange rates, citing pricing headwinds and market dynamics as significant challenges. The 2026 guidance reflects adjusted sales and profit decline due to pricing pressures, Medicaid coverage losses, and patent expiries.\n\nInternational operations are entering 2026 with a run rate of around 10% growth in the second half of 2025. However, the residual leaves the US growth to be in the teens in terms of sales decline.\n\n## Key Highlights\n\n**Q4 2025 Performance:**\nNovo Nordisk delivered 10% sales growth and 6% operating profit growth in 2025, led by 31% growth in obesity care and strong international GLP-1 volumes.\n\n**Product Launches and Regulatory Updates:**\nBy late 2025, Novo Nordisk received FDA approval for the Wegovy pill, the first oral GLP-1 for obesity, and submitted CagriSema in the U.S. The company expects Medicare Part D coverage for obesity medicines by mid-2026, which could positively impact future sales.\n\n**Market Access:**\nNovo Nordisk launched NovoCare Pharmacy in March 2025, and the company anticipates that coverage will begin around the middle of the year.\n\n**Patient Reach:**\nThe company is treating nearly 46 million people with its innovative medicines, reflecting Novo Nordisk's commitment to innovation and the ongoing efforts to expand access to its therapies worldwide.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2207cdf7-0767-4a59-9a1b-a30564847c67","uuid":"ab99b0b5-e20b-4b59-a3de-26a91efdcea8","timestamp":"2026-04-28T23:22:54.729Z","tool_use_result":{"query":"Novo Nordisk Q4 2025 earnings call transcript guidance 2026 key highlights","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01Vfty8j4RmVg12Y6s9GjjJN","content":[{"title":"Financial results and events overview - Novo Nordisk","url":"https://www.novonordisk.com/investors/financial-results.html"},{"title":"Earnings call transcript: Novo Nordisk Q4 2025 beats EPS and revenue forecasts By Investing.com","url":"https://www.investing.com/news/transcripts/earnings-call-transcript-novo-nordisk-q4-2025-beats-eps-and-revenue-forecasts-93CH-4484819"},{"title":"Q4 2025 Novo Nordisk A/S Earnings Call Transcript","url":"https://www.gurufocus.com/stock/XTER:NOV/transcripts/8582161"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S (NOVO:CA) Q4 2025 Earnings Call Transcript | Seeking Alpha","url":"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4866503-novo-nordisk-a-s-novo-ca-q4-2025-earnings-call-transcript"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S (NYSE:NVO) Q4 2025 Earnings Call Transcript - Insider Monkey","url":"https://www.insidermonkey.com/blog/novo-nordisk-a-s-nysenvo-q4-2025-earnings-call-transcript-1690199/"},{"title":"NOVO NORDISK A/S (NVON.MX) Q4 FY2025 earnings call transcript","url":"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NVON.MX/earnings/NVON.MX-Q4-2025-earnings_call-373247.html"},{"title":"NOVO-NORDISK AS I (NOVA.F) Q4 FY2025 earnings call transcript","url":"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NOVA.F/earnings/NOVA.F-Q4-2025-earnings_call-373247.html"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S Q4 2025 Earnings Call Transcript","url":"https://www.marketbeat.com/earnings/reports/2026-2-3-novo-nordisk-as-stock/"},{"title":"Novo Nordisk A/S – Transcripts – BamSEC","url":"https://www.bamsec.com/companies/353278/novo-nordisk-a-s/transcripts"},{"title":"Novo-Nordisk AS (NOV.SG) Q4 FY2025 earnings call transcript","url":"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NOV.SG/earnings/NOV.SG-Q4-2025-earnings_call-373247.html"}]},"Based on the Q4 2025 earnings call transcript, here are the key highlights and 2026 guidance for Novo Nordisk:\n\n## 2026 Guidance\n\nNovo Nordisk anticipates adjusted sales growth between -5% and -13% at constant exchange rates, citing pricing headwinds and market dynamics as significant challenges. The 2026 guidance reflects adjusted sales and profit decline due to pricing pressures, Medicaid coverage losses, and patent expiries.\n\nInternational operations are entering 2026 with a run rate of around 10% growth in the second half of 2025. However, the residual leaves the US growth to be in the teens in terms of sales decline.\n\n## Key Highlights\n\n**Q4 2025 Performance:**\nNovo Nordisk delivered 10% sales growth and 6% operating profit growth in 2025, led by 31% growth in obesity care and strong international GLP-1 volumes.\n\n**Product Launches and Regulatory Updates:**\nBy late 2025, Novo Nordisk received FDA approval for the Wegovy pill, the first oral GLP-1 for obesity, and submitted CagriSema in the U.S. The company expects Medicare Part D coverage for obesity medicines by mid-2026, which could positively impact future sales.\n\n**Market Access:**\nNovo Nordisk launched NovoCare Pharmacy in March 2025, and the company anticipates that coverage will begin around the middle of the year.\n\n**Patient Reach:**\nThe company is treating nearly 46 million people with its innovative medicines, reflecting Novo Nordisk's commitment to innovation and the ongoing efforts to expand access to its therapies worldwide."],"durationSeconds":6.891936249999999}}
